kets%20of%20air-defense%20systems%20make%20the%20airspace%20inhospitable.%20And%20even%20though%20Russia%20has%20a%20vastly%20larger%20air%20force%2C%20other%20issues%20may%20keep%20it%20from%20operating%20effectively%2C%20according%20to%20two%20NATO%20air%20commanders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20speech%20at%20the%20Global%20Air%20%26amp%3B%20Space%20Chiefs'%20Conference%20in%20London%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20Rich%20Knighton%2C%20chief%20of%20the%20British%20air%20staff%2C%20said%20Russia's%20land%20force%20is%20now%20%26quot%3Bweaker%2C%26quot%3B%20having%20lost%20more%20than%20two-thirds%20of%20its%20tanks%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20the%20air%20force%20remains%20largely%20intact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKnighton%20displayed%20graphics%20depicting%20both%20side's%20losses%2C%20based%20on%20assessments%20by%20British%20Defence%20Intelligence%20and%20open-source%20tracking%20website%20Oryx.%20One%20graphic%20said%20Russia%20has%20taken%20over%20220%2C000%20casualties%2C%20including%20176%20military%20pilots%2C%20and%20lost%20162%20air-defense%20systems.%20A%20second%20graphic%20said%20Russia's%20air%20force%20retains%2096%25%20of%20its%202%2C021%20fixed-wing%20aircraft%20and%2090%25%20of%20its%20899%20helicopters%2C%20with%20losses%20of%2086%20planes%20and%2090%20helicopters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Royal%20Air%20Force%20Knighton%20Russian%20losses%20Ukraine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b1a49ef9a25900194767b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22989%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERoyal%20Air%20Force%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20Rich%20Knighton%20at%20the%20Global%20Air%20%26amp%3B%20Space%20Chiefs%E2%80%99%20Conference%20on%20July%2013%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20and%20Space%20Power%20Association%20via%20YouTube%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20graphic%20noted%20heavier%20losses%20for%20Ukraine's%20air%20force%3A%2068%20fixed-wing%20airc