This%20is%20a%20very%20important%20aspect%20of%20India-UAE%20cooperation.%20It%20paves%20the%20way%20for%20enhanced%20economic%20collaboration%20and%20will%20make%20international%20financial%20interactions%20simpler.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBesides%2C%20the%20education%20ministries%20of%20the%20two%20countries%20and%20IIT-Delhi%20decided%20to%20establish%20a%20branch%20of%20the%20premier%20institute%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThis%20marks%20a%20significant%20stride%20in%20our%20educational%20internationalisation%20and%20is%20testament%20to%20India's%20innovation%20prowess.%20Education%20is%20the%20bond%20that%20unites%20us%2C%20it's%20the%20spark%20that%20ignites%20innovation.%20Together%2C%20we%20will%20leverage%20this%20power%20for%20mutual%20prosperity%20and%20global%20betterment%2C%26quot%3B%20tweeted%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPM%20Modi%20flew%20to%20Abu%20Dhabi%20this%20morning%20from%20France%20and%20held%20talks%20with%20UAE%20Crown%20Prince%20Sheikh%20Mohamed%20bin%20Zayed%20Al%20Nahyan%2C%20who%20received%20him%20at%20the%20airport%20on%20his%20arrival.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20always%20gladdening%20to%20meet%20HH%20Sheikh%20Mohamed%20bin%20Zayed%20Al%20Nahyan.%20His%20energy%20and%20vision%20for%20development%20are%20admirable.%20We%20discussed%20the%20full%20range%20of%20India-UAE%20ties%20including%20ways%20to%20boost%20cultural%20and%20economic%20ties%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20tweeted.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20said%20there%20was%20a%2020%25%20increase%20in%20India-UAE%20trade%20since%20the%20two%20countries%20signed%20the%20Comprehensive%20Economic%20Partnership%20Agreement%20last%20year.%20His%20remarks%20came%20following%20his%20meeting%20with%20the%20UAE%20President.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20he%20got%20the%20love%20of%20a%20brother%20from%20Mr%20Al%20Nahyan%20and%20that%20Indians%20see%20him%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btrue%20friend%26quot%3