l%2C%20came%20down%20to%20207.43%20metres%20by%2010%20am%20on%20Saturday%20from%20its%20peak%20of%20208.66%20metres%20at%208%20pm%20on%20Thursday%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Central%20Water%20Commission.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20still%20over%20two%20metres%20above%20the%20danger%20mark%20of%20205.33%20metres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20said%20the%20work%20is%20on%20to%20open%20the%20five%20gates%20of%20Yamuna%20Barrage%20to%20help%20drain%20out%20floodwater.%20%26quot%3BThe%20first%20jammed%20gate%20of%20the%20ITO%20Barrage%20has%20been%20opened.%20Soon%20all%20the%20five%20gates%20will%20be%20opened%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20water%20level%20in%20the%20Yamuna%20is%20receding.%20The%20situation%20will%20be%20normal%20soon%20if%20it%20doesn't%20rain.%20If%20it%20rains%2C%20then%20it%20may%20take%20a%20bit%20longer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20asked%20people%20to%20remain%20cautious%20and%20help%20each%20other.%20%26quot%3BThe%20threat%20of%20flood%20is%20not%20over%20yet.%20The%20flow%20of%20water%20is%20very%20strong%20and%20the%20water%20level%20can%20rise%20anytime%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Metro%20Rail%20Corporation%20(DMRC)%20has%20lifted%20the%20speed%20restriction%20for%20metro%20trains%20while%20crossing%20the%20bridges%20over%20the%20Yamuna%20and%20said%20that%20all%20trains%20are%20running%20at%20normal%20speed%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDMRC%20had%20earlier%20reduced%20the%20speed%20of%20metro%20trains%20over%20four%20Yamuna%20bridges%20amid%20rising%20water%20levels%20in%20the%20river.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20and%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20(NDRF)%20were%20also%20called%20in%20as%20the%20water%20submerged%20key%20areas%20of%20central%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689426120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fludhd8rg_yamuna-water-level-delhi-flood-_625x300_15_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-flood-yamuna-retreats-watch-how-much-yamuna-water-level-has-fallen-4210590%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20water%20levels%20in%20the%20Yamuna%20river%20began%20receding%20on%20Friday%20after%20rising%20continuously%20over%20the%20last%20three%20days.%20In%20the%20video%2C%20the%20water%20marks%20on%20the%20wall%20show%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20the%20water%20levels%20have%20fallen.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-flood-yamuna-retreats-watch-how-much-yamuna-water-level-has-fallen-4210590%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-flood-yamuna-retreats-watch-how-much-yamuna-water-level-has-fallen-4210590%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-flood-yamuna-retreats-watch-how-much-yamuna-water-level-has-fallen-4210590%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Wagner%20mercenaries%20have%20arrived%20in%20Belarus%2C%20Ukraine%20confirms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689425933000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F160C5%2Fproduction%2F_130390309_db1ae902fd4d13dca3e606556d822bd2dc65cf73-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66211121%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20June's%20mutiny%2C%20Wagner%20troops%20were%20told%20they%20could%20join%20the%20regular%20Russian%20army%20or%20head%20to%20Belarus.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A56%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66211121%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66211121.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66211121.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Noida%20Floods%3A%20Stranded%20To%20Die%2C%20500%20Workers%20Rescued%20From%20Illegal%20Farmhouses%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20thousands%20of%20people%20impacted%20by%20the%20floods%20along%20Yamuna%20banks%20in%20Noida%20this%20week%2C%20there%20were%20hundreds%20who%20were%20hired%20as%20help%20in%20farmhouses%20built%20illegally%20in%20the%20low-lying%20areas%20near%20the%20river%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20officials%20said%20the%20workers%20and%20staffers%20of%20the%20farmhouses-thousands%20in%20number%20-%20were%20not%20moved%20to%20safety%20in%20time%2C%20even%20though%20advisories%20were%20issued%20well%20before%20the%20area%20got%20inundated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20farmhouses%20are%20located%20near%20Nagli%20Wajidpur%20village%20in%20Sector%20135%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20pushta%20(embankment)%20towards%20the%20Yamuna%20-%20some%20two%20kilometres%20off%20the%20Noida-Greater%20Noida%20Expressway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-navy-working-round-the-clock-to-stop-yamuna-flooding-in-delhi-4209756%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20Army%2C%20Navy%20Working%20Round-The-Clock%20To%20Stop%20Yamuna%20Flooding%20In%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20than%20500%20such%20people%20were%20evacuated%20on%20Thursday%20and%20Friday%20from%20the%20farmhouses.%20As%20water%20entered%20the%20ground%2C%20many%20of%20those%20stranded%2C%20including%20women%2C%20had%20taken%20shelter%20on%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20the%20farmhouses.%20They%20carried%20some%20food%20and%20water%20with%20them%2C%20which%20had%20started%20to%20run%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20officer%20engaged%20in%20rescue%20and%20relief%20measures%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20these%20stranded%20people%20were%20discovered%20on%20Thursday%20when%20top%20police%20officers%20and%20administration%20officials%20took%20a%20boat%20ride%20deep%20into%20the%20flooded%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20teams%20of%20the%20National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%2C%20the%20State%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%2C%20the%20Provincial%20Armed%20Constabulary%2C%20the%20Noida%20Police%2C%20the%20Fire%20Brigade%2C%20the%20Noida%20Authority%2C%20and%20local%20village%20residents%20were%20engaged%20in%20rescue%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20structures%20in%20the%20floodplains%20are%20illegally%20constructed.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20we%20demolished%20over%20250%20farmhouses%20in%20anti-encroachment%20drives.%20A%20survey%20estimated%20the%20presence%20of%20around%20500-600%20more%20such%20illegal%20structures%2C%20against%20which%20action%20would%20be%20ensured%20in%20coming%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20Noida%20Authority%20CEO%20Ritu%20Maheshwari%20told%20PTI%20during%20an%20inspection%20of%20the%20site%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20said%20that%20the%20owners%20of%20many%20of%20the%20farmhouses%20have%20moved%20court%20to%20get%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20demolition%20of%20their%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20Magistrate%20Manish%20Kumar%20Verma%20said%20550%20hectares%20of%20land%20in%20Gautam%20Buddh%20Nagar%20got%20submerged%20in%20water%20due%20to%20the%20floods.%20People%20in%20the%20Jewar%20area%20of%20Greater%20Noida%20along%20Yamuna%20and%20those%20settled%20along%20Hindon%20were%20also%20impacted%20due%20to%20the%20floods%2C%20but%20the%20most%20affected%20were%20those%20in%20Noida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdvisories%20were%20being%20issued%20to%20the%20people%20inhabiting%20the%20low-lying%20regions%20here%20for%20the%20past%2010%20days%20when%20heavy%20rainfall%20started%20in%20the%20region%20and%20water%20levels%20in%20the%20rivers%20rose.%20Despite%20this%2C%20many%20stayed%20back%20and%20did%20not%20move%20to%20safety%20in%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Verma%2C%20who%20visited%20the%20site%20several%20times%20on%20Thursday%20and%20Friday%2C%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaushalya%2C%20around%2050%2C%20said%20she%20worked%20at%20a%20farmhouse%20but%20was%20left%20behind%20with%20no%20help%20until%20a%20team%20of%20rescuers%20brought%20her%20and%20her%20husband%20back%20to%20safety%20Friday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20and%20my%20husband%20were%20stuck%20in%20the%20farmhouse.%20We%20both%20feel%20safe%20now%20and%20are%20thankful%20to%20those%20who%20saved%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaushalya%20told%20PTI%20as%20she%20alighted%20from%20a%20boat%20on%20a%20partially%20submerged%20road%20leading%20to%20the%20string%20of%20farmhouses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20embankment%2C%20some%20of%20the%20rescued%20people%20now%20live%20in%20temporary%20structures%20with%20tarpaulin%20as%20a%20roof%20to%20shelter%20them.%20One%20of%20them%2C%20Shiv%20Pal%2C%20around%2045%2C%20said%20he%20was%20working%20at%20a%20farmhouse%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20moved%20out%20just%20in%20time%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20live%20here%20and%20work%20to%20make%20some%20money%20because%20we%20have%20two%20daughters%20who%20are%20to%20be%20married.%20The%20daughters%20live%20back%20home%20in%20Shahjahanpur%2C%26quot%3B%20Shiv%20Pal's%20wife%20said%2C%20as%20the%20couple%20waited%20to%20return%20to%20work%20in%20the%20farmhouse%20once%20the%20water%20subsided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAltogether%2C%20by%20Friday%20evening%2C%207%2C210%20people%20had%20been%20impacted%20by%20the%20floods%20as%20the%20overflowing%20Yamuna%20inundated%20around%20550%20hectares%20of%20low-lying%20land%20along%20its%20banks%20in%20Noida%20and%20Greater%20Noida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20impacted%20people%2C%203%2C610%20have%20been%20displaced%20and%20moved%20to%20shelter%20homes%2C%20where%20arrangements%20for%20their%20stay%2C%20food%2C%20water%2C%20and%20medications%20were%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%205%2C974%20animals%2C%20including%20cattle%2C%20dogs%2C%20rabbits%2C%20ducks%2C%20roosters%2C%20and%20guinea%20pigs%2C%20have%20also%20been%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20waterlogged%20areas%20to%20safety%20since%20Thursday%2C%20according%20to%20official%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689425100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fie89o3q8_aerial-view-of-farmhouses-in-a-floodaffected-area-in-noida_625x300_15_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnoida-floods-stranded-to-die-500-workers-rescued-from-illegal-farmhouses-4210007%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20of%20these%20stranded%20people%20were%20discovered%20on%20Thursday%20when%20top%20police%20officers%20and%20administration%20officials%20took%20a%20boat%20ride%20deep%20into%20the%20flooded%20areas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnoida-floods-stranded-to-die-500-workers-rescued-from-illegal-farmhouses-4210007%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnoida-floods-stranded-to-die-500-workers-rescued-from-illegal-farmhouses-4210007%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnoida-floods-stranded-to-die-500-workers-rescued-from-illegal-farmhouses-4210007%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Left%E2%80%99s%20Rising%20Vote%20Share%20Spells%20Trouble%20for%20BJP%20in%20Bengal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15180344%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-08-at-11.11.35-AM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20slow%20but%20steady%20rise%20in%20the%20Left%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20may%20hurt%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20chances%20of%20a%20good%20show%20in%20West%20Bengal%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20trends%20of%20the%20recently%20concluded%20three-tier%20panchayat%20elections%20indicate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20analysis%20of%20the%20results%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fpolitics%2Fbengal-panchayat-polls-tmc-position-violence%3Futm%3Dauthorlistpage%5C%22%3Epanchayat%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20civic%20polls%20in%20areas%20that%20fall%20under%20four%20BJP-held%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituencies%20reveals%20that%20the%20Left-Congress%20can%20spoil%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20chances%2C%20just%20as%20they%20did%20in%20dozens%20of%20zila%20parishad%20and%20hundreds%20of%20panchayat%20samiti%20and%20gram%20panchayat%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20swept%20the%20elections%20by%20securing%2051.5%25%20of%20polled%20votes%20%E2%80%93%20they%20won%2095%25%20of%20Zilla%20parishad%20(ZP)%20seats%20(835%20of%20876%20and%2052%20results%20were%20yet%20to%20be%20officially%20declared)%2C%2078.84%25%20of%20panchayat%20samiti%20seats%20(6%2C716%20of%208%2C518%20seats%20and%201%2C210%20results%20were%20yet%20to%20be%20officially%20declared)%2C%20and%2065.69%25%20of%20gram%20panchayat%20seats%20(35%2C606%20of%2054%2C195%20and%20another%209%2C027%20results%20were%20yet%20to%20be%20officially%20declared).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20for%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20strikingly%20high%20share%20of%20seats%20compared%20to%20the%20vote%20share%20is%20that%20the%20opposition%20votes%20got%20divided%2C%20often%20sharply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20most%20cases%2C%20they%20were%20split%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Left%20and%20in%20some%20cases%20with%20the%20Congress%20as%20another%20factor.%20This%20is%20the%20biggest%20cause%20of%20concern%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20as%20its%20impressive%20performance%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20emergence%20as%20the%20main%20opposition%20party%20in%20the%202021%20assembly%20election%20were%20made%20possible%20due%20to%20the%20consolidation%20of%20opposition%20votes%20in%20its%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20combined%20vote%20share%20of%20the%20Left%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Indian%20Secular%20Front%20(ISF)%20%E2%80%93%20which%20stood%20at%20a%20meagre%2010%25%20in%20the%202021%20assembly%20election%20%E2%80%93%20has%20crossed%20the%2020%25%20mark%20in%20the%20panchayat%20election.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20share%20was%20down%20to%2023%25%2C%20from%2040%25%20in%202019%20and%2038%25%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20many%20political%20observers%2C%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20and%20seat%20share%20both%20appear%20inflated%20due%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbengal-panchayat-election-violence-2%5C%22%3Escale%20of%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20alleged%20electoral%20malpractices%20that%20marred%20the%20rural%20polls%20%E2%80%93%20over%2040%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20pre-poll%2C%20poll-day%20and%20post-poll%20violence.%20They%20expect%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20to%20go%20down%20by%20a%20few%20percentage%20points%20when%20the%20elections%20are%20held%20under%20the%20watch%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20in%20multiple%20phases%20and%20with%20greater%20security%20cover.%20The%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20the%202021%20assembly%20elections%20stood%20at%2043%25%20and%2048%25%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20possibility%20does%20not%20provide%20the%20BJP%20with%20any%20relief%20because%20the%20Left%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20is%20coming%20uncomfortably%20close%20to%20its%20own%20%E2%80%93%20creating%20a%20sharp%20divide%20in%20opposition%20votes.%20This%20rise%20in%20Left%20vote%20share%20is%20also%20consistent%20with%20the%20trends%20of%20the%20post-2021%20assembly%20election%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnot-just-tmc-the-left-too-can-hurt-bjp-in-the-bengal-civic-polls%5C%22%3Ebypolls%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2Ftmc-supremacy-to-continue-as-bengal-re-enters-a-phase-of-divided-opposition-news-191991%5C%22%3E2022%20civic%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20in%20both%20cases%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumber%20game%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20stood%20at%2022.9%25%2C%20winning%2018.24%25%20of%20gram%20panchayat%20seats%2C%2012.25%25%20of%20panchayat%20samiti%20seats%20and%2026%20zilla%20parishad%20seats.%20The%20Left%2C%20with%20a%2013.2%25%20vote%20share%2C%20won%205.8%25%20of%20gram%20panchayat%20seats%2C%202.3%25%20of%20panchayat%20samiti%20seats%20and%202%20zilla%20parishad%20seats.%20The%20Congress%2C%20with%20a%206.42%25%20vote%20share%2C%20won%204.82%25%20of%20gram%20panchayat%20seats%2C%203.2%25%20of%20panchayat%20samiti%20seats%20and%2012%20zilla%20parishad%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20the%20Congress%20won%20more%20seats%20than%20the%20Left%20despite%20a%20smaller%20vote%20share%20is%20that%20their%20strength%20is%20concentrated%20mostly%20in%20the%20districts%20of%20Malda%20and%20Murshidabad%2C%20where%20their%20share%20of%20votes%20was%20significantly%20high%2C%20whereas%20the%20Left%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20is%20spread%20across%20several%20districts%2C%20mostly%20in%20central%20and%20south%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13152324%2FScreenshot-2023-07-13-at-3.22.09.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13152324%2FScreenshot-2023-07-13-at-3.22.09.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13152324%2FScreenshot-2023-07-13-at-3.22.09-300x148.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13152324%2FScreenshot-2023-07-13-at-3.22.09-1024x506.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663004%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22593%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFlags%20of%20TMC%20and%20CPI(M)%20in%20rural%20Bengal%20on%20panchayat%20poll%20day.%20Photo%3A%20Joydeep%20Sarkar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20several%20central%20and%20south%20Bengal%20districts%20%E2%80%93%20the%20region%20with%2034%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%2042%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Left%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20stood%20above%2016%25.%20This%20cost%20the%20BJP%20dozens%20of%20Zilla%20Parishad%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20CPI(M)%2C%20too%2C%20lost%20several%20seats%20due%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share.%20In%20both%20cases%2C%20the%20TMC%20benefitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20look%20at%20the%20results%20of%20East%20Midnapore%20district%20%E2%80%93%20home%20district%20of%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20where%20the%20BJP%20put%20up%20their%20best%20performance%20in%20the%20rural%20polls%20%E2%80%93%20shows%20that%20of%20the%2070%20seats%2C%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20winning%20margin%20over%20the%20BJP%20was%20lesser%20than%20the%20Left%E2%80%99s%20vote%20in%20as%20many%20as%2024%20seats.%20Finally%2C%20the%20TMC%20won%2055%20and%20the%20BJP%2012%20(three%20seats%20yet%20to%20be%20officially%20declared).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20in%20the%20three%20zilla%20parishad%20seats%20in%20Kolaghat%20block%2C%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20winning%20margin%20over%20the%20BJP%20stood%20at%206%2C430%20votes%2C%204%2C838%20votes%2C%20and%208%2C934%20votes%2C%20whereas%20in%20these%20seats%20the%20Left%E2%80%99s%20vote%20stood%20at%209%2C788%2C%209011%20and%2011%2C147%2C%20respectively.%20In%20the%20two%20seats%20in%20Nandakumar%20block%2C%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20winning%20margins%20stood%20at%20741%20and%20252%2C%20whereas%20the%20Left%20secured%206%2C301%20votes%20and%208%2C177%20votes%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20zilla%20parishad%20seat%20number%2019%20in%20Mahishadal%2C%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20winning%20margin%20was%202%2C689%20votes%2C%20while%20the%20CPI(M)%20got%205%2C014%20votes%2C%20spoiling%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20chances.%20In%20seat%20number%2024%20in%20Sutahata%2C%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20winning%20margin%20stood%20at%201%2C451%20votes%2C%20while%20the%20CPI(M)%20got%207%2C800%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Nadia%20district%2C%20which%20has%2052%20ZP%20seats%2C%20either%20the%20BJP%20or%20the%20Left%20lost%2024%20ZP%20seats%20due%20to%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%2C%20and%20in%20Hooghly%2C%20which%20has%2053%20ZP%20seats%2C%20there%20were%2011%20such%20ZP%20seats.%20Such%20trends%20were%20observed%20in%20all%20districts.%20Even%20in%20the%20north%20Bengal%20district%20of%20Cooch%20Behar%20where%20the%20Left%20is%20quite%20weak%2C%20the%20BJP%20lost%20seven%20seats%20due%20to%20the%20Left%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbengal-panchayat-election-tea-garden%5C%22%3EWhy%20There%E2%80%99s%20No%20One%20Left%20to%20Vote%20in%20North%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Tea%20Gardens%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Nadia%2C%20ZP%20seat%20number%2043%20in%20Ranaghat%20recorded%2038%2C523%20votes%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20TMC%2C%2024%2C853%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%2015%2C516%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Left.%20The%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20winning%20margin%20was%20less%20than%20the%20Left%E2%80%99s%20votes.%20In%20ZP%20seat%20number%2045%20in%20the%20Chakdah%20area%2C%20the%20TMC%2C%20BJP%20and%20Left%20votes%20stood%20at%2028%2C266%2C%2018%2C932%20and%2010%2C032%2C%20respectively.%20In%20ZP%20seat%20number%201%20in%20Hooghly%20district%20at%20Serampore-Uttarpara%20block%2C%20the%20TMC%2C%20The%20Left%20and%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20votes%20stood%20at%2012%2C703%2C%209%2C361%20and%208%2C685%2C%20respectively%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20spoiling%20the%20Left%E2%80%99s%20chances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13152647%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-08-at-11.13.59-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13152647%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-08-at-11.13.59-AM.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13152647%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-08-at-11.13.59-AM-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13152647%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-08-at-11.13.59-AM-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663006%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22607%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPeople%20queue%20to%20vote%20in%20Junglemahal%2C%20Bengal.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20block-wise%20results%20of%20ZP%20seats%20(blocks%20usually%20have%202-3%20ZP%20seats)%2C%20in%20Jangipara%20and%20Haripal%20of%20Hooghly%20district%20where%20the%20TMC%20was%20way%20ahead%20of%20both%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20and%20the%20Left%20stood%20nearly%20neck%20and%20neck%20%E2%80%93%20in%20Jangipara%20the%20Left%E2%80%99s%2027932%20was%20slightly%20above%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%2026%2C480%20and%20in%20Haripal%20BJP%E2%80%99s%2037%2C509%20was%20a%20little%20above%20the%20Left%E2%80%99s%2030%2C478.%20Jangipara%20falls%20in%20Serampore%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Haripal%20in%20Arambag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ZP-wise%20result%20of%20Gangajalghati%20block%20in%20Bankura%20district%20shows%20the%20following%20vote%20share%20%E2%80%93%2053%2C021%20(46%25)%2C%20BJP%2043%2C145%20(37.41%25)%2C%20Left%20%E2%80%93%2017%2C187%2C%20(14.9)%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%201%2C969.%20In%20Indpur%20block%20of%20the%20same%20district%2C%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20votes%20stood%20at%2044%2C134%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20at%2030%2C446%20and%20the%20Left%E2%80%99s%20at%2020%2C012.%20In%20Hirabandh%20and%20Khatra%20blocks%2C%20the%20Left%20and%20the%20BJP%20played%20spoilsport%20for%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20big%20picture%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20way%20to%20get%20the%20Lok%20Sabha-wise%20picture%20of%20local%20body%20election%20results%20is%20to%20add%20the%20figures%20for%20the%20Zilla%20parishad%20seats%2C%20the%20highest%20tier%20of%20the%20panchayat%20system%2C%20as%20the%20ZP%20seats%20are%20considered%20to%20reflect%20the%20closest%20trend%20to%20assembly%20election%20voting%20patterns.%20Each%20assembly%20is%20made%20of%20two%20to%20four%20ZP%20seats%20and%20sometimes%20urban%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELok%20Sabha-specific%20results%20of%20the%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20civic%20polls%20and%20the%20recent%20panchayat%20elections%20show%20that%20in%20Hooghly%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20won%20in%202019%20with%20a%20margin%20of%2073%2C000%20votes%2C%20the%20Left%20and%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20cumulative%20votes%20secured%20in%20urban%20and%20rural%20elections%20stand%20above%20what%20the%20BJP%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhy-bengals-panchayat-polls-will-be-different-this-year%5C%22%3EWhy%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Panchayat%20Polls%20Will%20Be%20Different%20This%20Year%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHooghly%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%20made%20of%2021%20ZP%20seats%20and%20three%20urban%20bodies%20%E2%80%93%20Chandannagar%20municipal%20corporation%2C%20Hooghly-Chinsurah%20municipality%20and%20Bansberia%20municipality.%20The%20results%20of%20these%2021%20zilla%20parishad%20seats%20show%20the%20TMC%20has%20got%205%2C93%2C217%20votes%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%20got%20271411%20votes%20and%20the%20Left%20secured%202%2C18%2C122.%20In%20the%202022%20urban%20elections%2C%20the%20TMC%20secured%201%2C40%2C009%20votes%2C%20the%20Left%20got%2077%2C003%20votes%20and%20the%20BJP%20polled%2031%2C568%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20vote%20stands%20at%207%2C33%2C226%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20at%203%2C02%2C979%20and%20the%20Left%E2%80%99s%20at%202%2C95%2C125.%20However%2C%20the%20Congress%20polled%20over%20another%2025%2C000%20votes%20in%20these%20polls.%20The%20Left-Congress%20combined%20votes%20are%20thus%20above%20what%20the%20BJP%20polled%20in%20the%20local%20elections.%20Even%20though%20the%20Left%20and%20the%20Congress%20mostly%20contested%20separately%20in%20the%20local%20body%20election%2C%20they%20are%20going%20together%20in%20most%20assembly%20or%20parliamentary%20elections%20and%20by-elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Left-Congress%20votes%20reflect%20a%20significant%20improvement%20in%20their%20performances%2C%20as%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20they%20polled%201%2C46%2C962%20votes%20fighting%20separately%20and%20in%202021%20secured%201%2C71%2C100%20votes%20in%20the%20seven%20seats%20that%20make%20up%20Hooghly%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20fighting%20in%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%20in%20Malda%20Uttar%20Lok%20Sabha%20of%20northern%20Bengal%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20won%20in%202019%20with%20a%20margin%20of%2084%2C288%20votes%2C%20the%20local%20body%20election%20statistics%20put%20the%20BJP%20at%20the%20third%20position.%20Habibpur%2C%20Bamangola%2C%20Gazole%2C%20Chanchal%20I%20and%20II%2C%20Harishchandrapur%20I%20and%20II%20and%20Ratua%20I%20and%20II%20community%20development%20blocks%20and%20Old%20Malda%20municipality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F22123105%2F20210415_132321.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F22123105%2F20210415_132321.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F22123105%2F20210415_132321-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F22123105%2F20210415_132321-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-524129%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EElection%20graffiti%20at%20a%20village%20in%20Gazole%2C%20Malda.%20Photo%3A%20File%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20zilla%20parishad%20seats%20that%20make%20up%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Old%20Maldah%20municipality%2C%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20votes%20stand%20at%204%2C59%2C536%2C%20the%20Left-Congress%20combined%20vote%20at%203%2C20%2C402%20and%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20at%20233%2C121.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20got%205%2C09%2C524%20votes%2C%20against%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%204%2C25%2C236%2C%20while%20the%20Left-Congress%20cumulative%20votes%20stood%20at%203%2C55%2C671.%20In%20the%202021%20assembly%20election%2C%20the%20TMC%2C%20BJP%20and%20Left-Congress%20alliance%E2%80%99%20votes%20stood%20at%207%2C46%2C681%20votes%2C%204%2C71%2C042%20votes%20and%201%2C51%2C060%20votes%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bishnupur%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20the%20Bankura%20district%20of%20southwestern%20Bengal%2C%20the%20Zilla%20parishad%20and%20civic%20body%20election%20results%20put%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20votes%20at%207%2C90%2C166%20votes%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20stood%20at%204%2C11%2C841%20and%20the%20Left-Congress%20combine%E2%80%99s%20at%202%2C32%2C760.%20Over%202%20lakh%20of%20this%20is%20the%20Left%E2%80%99s%20vote.%20Barjora%2C%20Gangajalghati%2C%20Onda%2C%20Bankura%20II%2C%20Bishnupur%2C%20Taldangra%2C%20Kotulpur%2C%20Joypur%2C%20Patrasayar%2C%20Indas%20and%20Sonamukhi%20blocks%20and%20Bishnupur%20and%20Sonamukhi%20municipalities%20make%20up%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202021%20assembly%20election%2C%20the%20cumulative%20vote%20share%20in%20the%20seven%20seats%20concerned%20was%206%2C77%2C147%20votes%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%206%2C48%2C438%20votes%20for%20the%20TMC%20and%201%2C25%2C686%20votes%20for%20the%20Left-Congress%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Ranaghat%20Lok%20Sabha%20of%20Nadia%20district%20in%20central%20Bengal%2C%20the%20local%20body%20election%20results%20put%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20votes%20at%207%2C05%2C022%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20at%204%2C24%2C538%20and%20the%20Left-Congress%E2%80%99%20at%202%2C02%2C912.%20Nabadwip%2C%20Santipur%2C%20Ranaghat%20I%20and%20II%2C%20Hanskhali%2C%20Chakdah%20and%20Krishnaganj%20blocks%20and%20Ranaghat%2C%20Birnagar%2C%20Santipur%2C%20Nabadwip%20and%20Chakdah%20municipalities%20and%20Taherpur%20notified%20area%20make%20up%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202021%20assembly%20election%2C%20the%20votes%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20TMC%20and%20the%20Left-Congress%20alliance%20stood%20at%207%2C60%2C040%20votes%2C%206%2C58%2C351%20votes%20and%2087%2C786%20votes%2C%20respectively.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20bagged%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20by%20securing%207%2C83%2C254%20votes%2C%20against%20the%20TMC%E2%80%99s%205%2C49%2C825%20and%20the%20Left-Congress%20total%20vote%20stood%20at%20only%201%2C21%2C068.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20political%20scientist%20Dwaipayan%20Bhattacharyya%2C%20who%20teaches%20at%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20and%20closely%20follows%20Bengal%20politics%2C%20the%20results%20are%20particularly%20bad%20for%20the%20BJP%20because%20the%20Left%20vote%20share%20increased%20despite%20widespread%20violence%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20failed%20to%20retain%20its%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20indicated%20there%20are%20two%20oppositions%20%E2%80%93%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20official%20opposition%20which%20is%20losing%20ground%2C%20and%20the%20emerging%20force%20of%20Left-Congress-Indian%20Secular%20Front%20(ISF)%20combine%20which%20is%20playing%20the%20real%20opposition%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20him%2C%20the%20panchayat%20election%20results%20assume%20significance%20because%20this%20situation%20is%20leading%20West%20Bengal%20to%20a%20phase%20of%20triangular%20contests.%20Politics%20here%20has%20traditionally%20remained%20bipolar.%20Even%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20TMC%20in%201998%2C%20it%20surged%20ahead%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20elections%20remained%20largely%20bipolar%2C%20a%20trend%20which%20continued%20even%20after%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%202014%2C%20he%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20results%20will%20depend%20on%20multiple%20national%20issues%2C%20including%20how%20the%20BJP%20plays%20out%20the%20politics%20around%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20inauguration%20and%20public%20sentiment%20over%20economic%20issues.%20But%20it%20would%20also%20depend%20significantly%20on%20how%20the%20Left-Congress%20combine%20manages%20to%20posit%20themselves%20as%20the%20real%20ideological%20opponent%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20as%20there%20is%20a%20clear%20indication%20of%20triangular%20contests%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhattacharyya%20told%20The%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689425028000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15180344%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-08-at-11.11.35-AM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbengal-panchayat-election-left-bjp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lok%20Sabha-wise%20analysis%20of%20panchayat%20and%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20civic%20polls%20show%20the%20Left-Congress%20vote%20share%20coming%20uncomfortably%20close%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbengal-panchayat-election-left-bjp%22%2C