C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espn.com%2Fwnba%2Fstory%2F_%2Fid%2F37602441%2Fwnba-expansion-everything-know-2023-season%5C%22%3Ethey%20will%20expand%20beyond%2012%20teams%20in%20the%20future%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aliyah%20Boston%20(right)%20and%20WNBA%20Commissioner%20Cathy%20Engelbert%20pose%20with%20an%20Indiana%20Fever%20jersey.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F643588c6ca216e0018210e3d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAliyah%20Boston%20(right)%20and%20WNBA%20Commissioner%20Cathy%20Engelbert%20pose%20with%20an%20Indiana%20Fever%20jersey%20during%20the%202023%20WNBA%20Draft.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FAdam%20Hunger%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20growth%20is%20due%2C%20in%20large%20part%2C%20to%20the%20increasing%20demand%20for%20live%20sports.%20As%20more%20streaming%20services%20enter%20the%20market%2C%20live%20sports%20give%20them%20two%20big%20wins%3A%201)%20adding%20a%20new%20type%20of%20content%20that%20brings%20in%20new%20subscribers%20and%20gives%20existing%20subs%20a%20reason%20to%20stick%20around%20%E2%80%94%20the%20something-for-everybody%20model%3B%20and%202)%20Live%20sports%2C%20like%20news%2C%20is%20a%20constant%20fount%20of%20content%20even%20beyond%20the%20games.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20seemingly%20insatiable%20need%20for%20programming%20is%20a%20big%20reason%20why%20North%20American%20newcomers%2C%20like%20Major%20League%20Rugby%20and%20Major%20League%20Cricket%2C%20also%20have%20a%20good%20shot%20at%20survival.%20While%20they%20have%20a%20steeper%20hill%20to%20climb%20than%20MLS%2C%20the%20skyrocketing%20growth%20of%20soccer%20shows%20that%20Americans%20are%20willing%20to%20embrace%20sports%20that%20have%20traditionally%20done%20much%20better%20in%20Europe.%20And%20we%20haven't%20even%20gotten%20to%20the%20spring%20pro%20football%20leagues%2C%20XFL%20and%20USFL.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaturation%3F%20Not%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20if%20there%20is%20a%20place%20on%20ESPN%2B%20for%20cornhole%20and%20kabaddi%20(for%20the%20latter%2C%20think%20a%20cross%20between%20tag%20and%20dodgeball%20with%20much%20more%20contact)%2C%20then%20there%20is%20a%20place%20for%20cricket%20and%20rugby.%20If%20your%20sport%20has%20a%20fan%20base%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20small%2C%20there%20is%20a%20good%20chance%20a%20streaming%20service%20will%20be%20willing%20to%20broadcast%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20if%20you%20have%20ever%20dreamed%20of%20having%20a%20pro%20sports%20team%20in%20your%20neighborhood%2C%20there's%20never%20been%20a%20better%20chance%20it%20might%20actually%20happen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-pro-sports-teams-expansion-nba-mlb-nhl-mls-streaming-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689424680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b181f99751e300192a2615%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-pro-sports-teams-expansion-nba-mlb-nhl-mls-streaming-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Big%20players%20like%20the%20NBA%20and%20MLB%20are%20eyeing%20expansion%2C%20and%20more%20leagues%20are%20being%20elevated%20to%20major-pro%20status%20thanks%20to%20streaming.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cgaines%40businessinsider.com%20(Cork%20Gaines)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-pro-sports-teams-expansion-nba-mlb-nhl-mls-streaming-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anti-LGBTQ%2B%20activism%20spiked%20during%20Pride%20Month%2C%20with%20California%20leading%20the%20way%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22enraged%20man%20pointing%20behind%20barrier%20next%20to%20sign%20that%20says%20%26quot%3BTeach%20ABC%20not%20LGBTQ%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b1829cf9a2590019475f2e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222499%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20anti-LGBTQ%2B%20demonstrator%20yells%20at%20pro-LGBTQ%2B%20demonstrators%20from%20behind%20a%20police%20barricade%20in%20Glendale%2C%20California.%3Cp%3EDavid%20McNew%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAnti-LGBTQ%2B%20activism%20spiked%20in%20June%2C%20according%20to%20the%20monitoring%20group%20ACLED.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPride%20Month%20saw%20more%20anti-LGBTQ%2B%20demonstrations%20than%20any%20other%20period%20since%202020.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20really%20about%20who%20belongs%20in%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20Vanderbilt%20professor%20Sophie%20Bjork-James%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20one%20thing%20for%20people%20to%20do%20as%20they%20like%20in%20the%20privacy%20of%20their%20own%20homes%2C%20the%20argument%20goes%2C%20but%20to%20a%20loud%20minority%20of%20Americans%20the%20act%20of%20stepping%20outside%20and%20existing%20as%20one's%20true%20self%20is%20a%20bridge%20too%20far.%20They%20now%20label%20calls%20for%20acceptance%20%26quot%3Bindoctrination%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bgrooming.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20community%20has%20become%20increasingly%20visible%20in%20entertainment%2C%20politics%2C%20and%20corporate%20America%2C%20there%20has%20been%20an%20accompanying%20spike%20in%20anti-LGBTQ%2B%20activism.%20Tangible%20evidence%20of%20cultural%20progress%20%E2%80%94%20a%20giant%20beer%20maker%20partnering%20with%20a%20transgender%20influencer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbud-light-backlash-anheuser-busch-us-ceo-we-hear-you-2023-6%5C%22%3Efor%20example%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20is%20now%20often%20met%20with%20fire%20and%20brimstone%20from%20right-wing%20campaigners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20new%20research%20found%20that%20the%20recent%20effort%20to%20roll%20back%20gains%20for%20gay%20and%20trans%20Americans%20spiked%20during%20Pride%20celebrations%2C%20including%20in%20%26quot%3Bblue%26quot%3B%20states%20such%20as%20California%2C%20which%20was%20home%20to%20a%20full%201%20in%205%20of%20the%20anti-LGBTQ%2B%20demonstrations%20last%20month%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Armed%20Conflict%20Location%20and%20Event%20Data%20Project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20past%20June%20saw%20the%20highest%20ever%20single-month%20level%20of%20anti-LGBTQ%2B%20demonstrations%20since%20ACLED%20began%20collecting%20data%20for%20the%20United%20States%20in%202020%2C%26quot%3B%20Kieren%20Doyle%2C%20the%20North%20America%20research%20manager%20for%20the%20group%2C%20told%20Insider.%20ACLED%20defines%20demonstrations%20as%20in-person%20events%20with%20three%20or%20more%20people.%20%26quot%3BThis%20new%20peak%20in%20our%20data%20comes%20after%20anti-LGBTQ%2B%20demonstrations%20had%20already%20surged%20to%20their%20highest%20point%20on%20record%20by%20late%202022.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWesley%20Phelps%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20history%20at%20the%20University%20of%20North%20Texas%20and%20host%20of%20the%20podcast%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.queeringthelonestarstate.com%2F%5C%22%3EQueering%20the%20Lone%20Star%20State%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20that%20it%20makes%20sense%20that%20actions%20targeting%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20community%20would%20increase%20following%20its%20dramatic%20inroads%20in%20the%202000s%2C%20including%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%202015%20decision%20in%20Obergefell%20v.%20Hodges%20that%20legalized%20same-sex%20marriage.%20Since%20then%2C%20much%20of%20the%20country%20has%20shifted%20from%20merely%20tolerating%20LGBTQ%2B%20people%20to%20accepting%20them%20and%20their%20increased%20visibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20put%20yourself%20in%20the%20mindset%20of%20an%20anti-LGBTQ%20person%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20there's%20not%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20reason%20for%20you%20to%20organize%20and%20demonstrate%20against%20the%20rights%20of%20queer%20people%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebecause%20there%20really%20weren't%20very%20many%2C%26quot%3B%20Phelps%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it's%20not%20only%20visibility%2C%20right%3F%20It's%20also%20queer%20people%20saying%20mainstream%20society%20needs%20to%20kind%20of%20rethink%20the%20way%20that%20they've%20thought%20about%20us%2C%20rethink%20the%20way%20they%20act%20around%20us%2C%20and%20rethink%20the%20way%20they%20trust%20us.%20That's%20asking%20something%20of%20people%20in%20a%20way%2C%20I%20think%2C%20that%20is%20just%20ripe%20for%20backlash.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAnti-LGBTQ%2B%20activism%20spikes%2C%20blue%20states%20included%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facleddata.com%2F2023%2F07%2F06%2Fregional-overview-united-states-canada-june-2023%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%20from%20ACLED%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwagner-russian-mercenaries-linked-to-killings-of-african-civilians-2022-9%5C%22%3Etracks%20violence%20in%20war%20zones%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20notes%20that%20while%20many%20demonstrations%20were%20billed%20as%20anti-Pride%2C%20they%20also%20targeted%20drag%20shows%20and%20gender-affirming%20care.%20Such%20actions%20were%20recorded%20in%2026%20states%20and%20the%20District%20of%20Columbia%2C%20but%20were%20concentrated%20in%20Texas%2C%20New%20York%2C%20and%20California%2C%20with%20just%20under%2020%25%20of%20recorded%20anti-LGBTQ%2B%20events%20taking%20place%20in%20the%20Golden%20State.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20finding%20comes%20after%20ACLED%20previously%20reported%20a%20more%20than%20300%25%20increase%20in%20anti-LGBTQ%2B%20actions%20by%20far-right%20extremists%20in%202022%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20year%20before%2C%20which%20it%20said%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busine