%3E%3Cp%3EI%20noticed%20a%20big%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20packages%20and%20stops%2C%20and%20they%20say%20that%20it's%20gonna%20go%20on%20this%20way%20up%20until%20the%20end%20of%20next%20week.%20So%20this%20week%20and%20next%20week%20especially%20are%20really%20heavy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20surge%20in%20ordering%20during%20the%2011th%20and%2012th%2C%20it%20takes%20like%20a%20week%20and%20a%20half%20to%20two%20weeks%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20backlog%20of%20all%20the%20orders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20I%20have%20173%20stops%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20little%20bit%20less%20busy%20than%20yesterday.%20Yesterday%2C%20I%20had%20closer%20to%20250%20locations%2C%20and%20I%20have%20308%20packages%20today.%20Typically%2C%20I%20would%20say%20it's%20like%20about%2050%20to%2075%20more%20packages%20and%20maybe%20like%2030%20more%20stops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20show%20up%20at%209%3A30%20a.m.%20but%20we%20normally%20don't%20leave%20the%20station%20until%2011%3A00%20a.m.%20It's%20not%20uncommon%20to%20reach%20our%20first%20stop%20at%2011%3A30.%20Usually%20I%20finish%20at%20like%206%20or%207%2C%20but%20last%20night%20for%20example%2C%20I%20didn't%20get%20finished%20until%20like%20after%208.%20It%20just%20takes%20a%20lot%20more%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20amount%20of%20packages%20and%20deliveries%20are%20crazy%20but%20we%20use%20bungee%20cords%20to%20keep%20all%20the%20packages%20in%20place%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amazon%20Prime%20packages%20are%20stacked%20high%20and%20held%20in%20place%20by%20bungee%20cords%20in%20vans%20during%20the%20Prime%20season.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b166c9f9a25900194757fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20DSP%20driver%20said%20that%20his%20company%20provides%20drivers%20with%20bungee%20cords%20to%20keep%20Amazon%20Prime%20packages%20in%20place%20during%20the%20Prime%20season.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20DSP%20driver%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20had%20way%20more%20totes%20that%20have%20packages%20in%20them.%20There's%20different%20ways%20of%20loading%20our%20vans%2C%20and%20they're%20encouraging%20us%20to%20triple-stack%20the%20totes.%20So%20there's%20a%20vertical%20column%20of%20three%20in%20a%20cargo%20van%20and%20that's%20kind%20of%20messy%20unless%20there's%20a%20way%20to%20restrain%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20they%20supplied%20us%20with%20bungee%20cords%20so%20we%20can%20lash%20the%20totes%20to%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20van%20so%20the%20totes%20don't%20tip%20over%20while%20you're%20driving.%20They%20gave%20us%20those%20tools%2C%20at%20least%2C%20to%20make%20it%20a%20little%20bit%20easier%20with%20all%20the%20increased%20packages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20it's%20as%20bad%20as%20it%20could%20be%2C%20but%20I%20mean%2C%20I'm%20just%20speaking%20for%20myself.%20For%20other%20people%20it%20might%20be%20worse%3A%20more%20stops%2C%20more%20locations%2C%20more%20packages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20try%20to%20take%20care%20of%20myself%20by%20taking%20breaks%2C%20staying%20hydrated%2C%20and%20taking%20ibuprofen%20and%20Tylenol%20for%20my%20body%20aches%20but%20the%20work%20is%20draining%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20gotten%20busier%20and%20it's%20really%20hot%20and%20humid.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20AC%20but%20we're%20not%20allowed%20to%20run%20the%20engines%20during%20stops.%20So%20whenever%20we%20turn%20off%20the%20engine%2C%20get%20the%20package%2C%20bring%20it%20to%20the%20door%20and%20go%20back%20to%20the%20van%2C%20it's%20really%20hot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBreaks%20are%20optional.%20They%20don't%20discourage%20us%20from%20taking%20breaks%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20necessarily%20%3Cem%3Eencourage%3C%2Fem%3E%20us%2C%20if%20that%20makes%20any%20sense.%20But%20since%20it's%20gotten%20busier%20in%20the%20past%20week%20or%20so%2C%20we're%20allowed%20two%2015-minute%20breaks%20and%20an%20unpaid%2030-minute%20lunch.%20I've%20been%20giving%20myself%20those%2015%20minutes%20to%20cool%20down%20and%20drink%20fluids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20owner%20and%20dispatchers%2C%20they%20encourage%20us%20to%20stay%20hydrated%20and%20take%20a%20break%20here%20and%20there%20if%20we%20need%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20advice%20to%20other%20drivers%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBe%20sure%20to%20be%20well%20rested%20and%20well%20hydrated%2C%20and%20just%20mentally%20prepare%20yourself%20for%20more%20stops%20and%20more%20packages%20so%20you're%20not%20completely%20overwhelmed%20when%20you're%20going%20out%20on%20the%20route.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20take%20ibuprofen%20and%20Tylenol%20if%20I'm%20aching%20during%20the%20route.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20definitely%2C%20really%20draining%20me.%20I'm%20already%20feeling%20really%20kind%20of%20run%20down%2C%20just%20very%20hot%20and%20sweaty%20and%20achy%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day.%20I%20spend%20time%20with%20my%20family%2C%20watch%20TV%2C%20take%20a%20nice%20shower%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20and%20just%20take%20my%20breaks%2C%20to%20not%20allow%20myself%20to%20get%20mentally%20and%20physically%20overwhelmed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20get%20paid%20time%20and%20a%20half%20for%20overtime%2C%20but%20don't%20think%20I%20would%20want%20to%20work%20during%20Prime%20again%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20getting%20paid%20overtime%20for%20like%20the%20extra%20days%20that%20we're%20working%20anything%20over%2040%20hours.%20But%20we%20don't%20have%20any%20other%20bonuses%20or%20incentives%20aside%20from%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYesterday%20they%20gave%20us%20a%20brown%20bag%20to%20have%20a%20bag%20of%20chips%2C%20an%20apple%2C%20and%20like%20one%20of%20those%20meat%20and%20cheese%20stick%20packages.%20So%20that's%20something%20they%20did%20for%20us%20that%20they%20normally%20don't%20do.%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20nice%20touch%2C%20but%20I%20mean%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20anything%20major%2C%20you%20know%3F%20Like%2C%20oh%20wow%2C%20look%20how%20well%20they're%20treating%20us.%20But%20it's%20a%20nice%20touch%2C%20I%20guess.%20A%20good%20gesture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20something%20that%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20I%20would%20like%20doing%20it%20again.%20I%20just%20don't%20think%20for%20the%20amount%20that%20we%20get%20paid%2C%20that%20the%20work%20is%20really%20worth%20it%20sometimes.%20I%20make%20%2419.50%20an%20hour%20and%20time%20and%20a%20half%20for%20overtime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelivery-driver-amazon-prime-day-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689423600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b1667df9a25900194757e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelivery-driver-amazon-prime-day-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20driver%20for%20one%20of%20Amazon's%20delivery%20partners%20told%20Insider%20about%20the%20steps%20he%20takes%20to%20make%20it%20through%20one%20of%20the%20busiest%20seasons%20of%20the%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ylee%40insider.com%20(Yeji%20Jesse%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelivery-driver-amazon-prime-day-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Dam%20And%20Barrage%20Different'%3A%20BJP%20After%20AAP%20Alleges%20Delhi%20Flood%20Conspiracy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20the%20Delhi%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20made%20public%20declarations%20of%20working%20together%20as%20a%20team%20and%20not%20indulging%20in%20a%20blame%20game%20during%20the%20crisis%2C%20the%20AAP%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20stepped%20up%20attacks%20on%20each%20other%20over%20the%20flood-like%20situation%20in%20Delhi.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20has%20alleged%20a%20conspiracy%20against%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20and%20blamed%20the%20BJP%20governments%20in%20Haryana%20and%20at%20the%20Centre.%20The%20charge%20led%20to%20a%20sharp%20rejoinder%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20said%20that%20the%20AAP%20thinks%20everyone%20is%20indulging%20in%20a%20conspiracy%2C%20but%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20is%20%26quot%3Bsitting%20in%20his%20%3Cem%3Esheesh%20mahal%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20air-conditioned%20comfort%26quot%3B%2C%20is%20doing%20the%20right%20thing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20joint%20press%20conference%20yesterday%2C%20which%20was%20meant%20to%20signal%20unity%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20and%20Delhi%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20had%20stressed%20on%20the%20need%20to%20work%20together%20as%20a%20team.%20%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20we%20need%20to%20work%20as%20a%20team.%20I%20can%20also%20say%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20but%20this%20is%20not%20what%20we%20should%20do%20at%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20LG%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20similar%20vein%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20such%20a%20crisis%20when%20humans%20should%20help%20other%20humans.%20There's%20no%20use%20abusing%20one%20another.%20BJP%20has%20been%20abusing%20me%20since%20yesterday.%20Let%20them%20do%20it%2C%20doesn't%20matter%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20seemed%20not%20to%20have%20reached%20AAP%20functionaries%2C%20however%2C%20with%20Delhi%20minister%20Saurabh%20Bhardwaj%20launching%20an%20all-out%20attack%20on%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP-led%20governments%20in%20Centre%20and%20Haryana%20are%20conspiring%20against%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi.%20They%20are%20deliberately%20attempting%20to%20cause%20a%20flood%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20question%20that%20arises%20is%20that%20if%20it%20has%20not%20been%20raining%20in%20Delhi%2C%20how%20is%20it%20that%20the%20water%20level%20in%20the%20Yamuna%20is%20a%20metre%20higher%20than%20the%20previous%20record%20high%20in%201978%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhardwaj%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20July%209%20to%2013%2C%20water%20was%20deliberately%20released%20towards%20Delhi%20as%20part%20of%20a%20conspiracy.%20Last%20year%2C%20in%20August%2C%20water%20was%20not%20only%20released%20towards%20Delhi%20but%20the%20eastern%20and%20western%20canals%20as%20well.%20The%20flow%20was%20evenly%20distributed%20between%20multiple%20states%2C%20because%20of%20which%20there%20was%20no%20flood%20in%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20news%20agency%20ANI%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn.%3Cbr%3E%5CnResponding%20to%20the%20charge%2C%20Haryana%20Chief%20Minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20said%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20had%20been%20told%20about%20the%20difference%20between%20a%20barrage%20and%20a%20dam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20region%20has%20received%20more%20rain%20than%20was%20expected%20or%20forecast.%20Rainfall%20in%20the%20hilly%20areas%20led%20to%20water%20levels%20increasing%20in%20our%20rivers.%20The%20Yamuna%20had%201%20lakh%20cusecs%20of%20water%2C%20which%20went%20up%20to%203.7%20lakh%20cusecs%20the%20next%20day.%20We%20had%20told%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20that%20it%20is%20a%20barrage%2C%20not%20a%20dam.%20A%20dam%20can%20stop%20water%2C%20a%20barrage%20can%20store%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Khattar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20water%20can%20be%20regulated%20in%20the%20barrage%20to%20a%20certain%20extent%20but%20it%20has%20a%20capacity%20of%201%20lakh%20cusecs.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20water%20crosses%20that%20level%2C%20it%20will%20naturally%20have%20to%20be%20released%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Khattar%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELashing%20out%20at%20the%20AAP%2C%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Gaurav%20Bhatia%20said%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20priority%20is%20not%20working%2C%20but%20making%20excuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20minister%2C%20who%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20working%2C%20is%20accusing%20everyone%20from%20the%20Army%20and%20%C2%A0National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20to%20the%20LG%20and%20the%20Centre%20-%20all%20of%20whom%20have%20been%20helping%20the%20people%2024X7%20-%20of%20conspiring.%20But%20the%20person%20who%20is%20sitting%20in%20his%20%3Cem%3Esheesh%20mahal%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20enjoying%20the%20air%20conditioning%20is%20right.%20That%20chief%20minister%20is%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhatia%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20chief%20minister%20is%20saying%203.5%20lakh%20cusecs%20of%20water%20have%20been%20released.%208%20lakh%20cusecs%20had%20been%20released%20in%202013%20and%202019%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20flooding.%20There's%20been%20a%20flood%20this%20time%20because%20the%20chief%20minister's%20priority%20is%20not%20working%2C%20but%20making%20excuses.%20He%20blamed%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20for%20pollution%20and%20migrants%20for%20the%20lack%20of%20beds%20during%20Covid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20been%20at%20loggerheads%20for%20years%20now%2C%20but%20the%20feud%20escalated%20in%20May%2C%20when%20the%20Centre%20passed%20an%20ordinance%20on%20the%20control%20of%20services%20in%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689423480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Ftaps1i98_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_14_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-flood-drowns-talk-of-teamwork-triggers-aap-bjp-slugfest-4210327%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20day%20after%20the%20Delhi%20LG%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20made%20public%20declarations%20of%20working%20together%20as%20a%20team%20and%20not%20indulging%20in%20a%20blame%20game%20during%20the%20crisis%2C%20the%20AAP%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20stepped%20up%20attacks%20on%20each%20other%20over%20the%20flood-like%20situation%20in%20Delhi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22c