Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20economy%20may%20avoid%20a%20recession%20after%20all.%20That's%20not%20great%20for%20sidelined%20homebuyers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20recession%20would%20likely%20cause%20interest%20rates%20to%20fall%2C%20bringing%20down%20mortgage%20rates%20and%20adding%20housing%20inventory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHigh%20borrowing%20costs%20and%20elevated%20prices%20are%20the%20new%20normal%20for%20now%2C%20one%20real%20estate%20economist%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20will%20probably%20avoid%20a%20recession%20after%20all%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%20could%20be%20bad%20news%20for%20buyers%20who%20are%20being%20priced%20out%20of%20a%20frustratingly%20unaffordable%20housing%20market%2C%20according%20to%20National%20Association%20of%20Realtors%20chief%20economist%20Lawrence%20Yun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20estate%20economist%20saw%20mortgage%20rates%20and%20home%20prices%20staying%20flat%E2%80%94which%20is%20to%20say%2C%20elevated%E2%80%94through%20the%20rest%20of%202023%2C%20with%20the%20the%2030-year-fixed%20mortgage%20rate%20easing%20to%20just%206%25-6.5%25%20by%20year-end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20seismic%20change%20some%20homebuyers%20are%20hoping%20for%2C%20with%20mortgage%20rates%20currently%20hovering%20near%207%25%20for%20most%20of%20the%20past%20year.%20That's%20partly%20the%20fault%20of%20the%20strong%20economy%2C%20Yun%20said%2C%20and%20the%20US%20averting%20a%20downturn%20will%20likely%20influence%20interest%20rates%20to%20stay%20high%20throughout%20the%20economy%2C%20meaning%20mortgage%20costs%20won't%20budge%20much%20from%2020-year%20highs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYun%20pointed%20to%20the%20robust%20labor%20market%2C%20with%20the%20economy%20adding%20209%2C000%20in%20June%2C%20only%20slightly%20lower%20than%20in%20previous%20months.%20Inflation%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20cooled%20significantly%20from%20its%2041-year-record%20last%20June%2C%20with%20prices%20accelerating%20just%203%25%20year-per-year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20baseline%20is%20we%20don't%20have%20a%20recession.%20We%20continue%20to%20crank%20out%20jobs%20%E2%80%93%20maybe%20not%20as%20strongly%20%E2%80%93%20but%20still%20more%20jobs%20with%20each%20passing%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20Yun%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20no%20recession%20suggests%20the%20Fed%20won't%20be%20compelled%20rapidly%20pull%20back%20interest%20rates%20to%20avoid%20exerting%20too%20much%20pressure%20on%20the%20economy.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmegroup.com%2Fmarkets%2Finterest-rates%2Fcme-fedwatch-tool.html%3Fredirect%3D%2Ftrading%2Finterest-rates%2Fcountdown-to-fomc.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInvestors%20think%20it's%20nearly%20certain%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Fed%20raises%20rates%20once%20more%20this%20month%20and%20then%20see%20a%20high%20likelihood%20that%20the%20central%20bank%20holds%20its%20benchmark%20rate%20steady%20at%205.25%25.5.50%25%20for%20the%20rest%20of%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20mean%20a%20longer%20waiting%20game%20for%20homebuyers%2C%20as%20the%20higher%20fed%20funds%20rate%20influence%20higher%20mortgage%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHigh%20rates%20have%20battered%20housing%20activity%20over%20the%20past%20year%20as%20buyers%20get%20pushed%20to%20the%20sidelines.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20high%20cost%20of%20borrowing%20has%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fhousing-market-outlook-inventory-redfin-home-prices-sale-economy-downturn-2023-4%5C%22%3Eworsened%20the%20inventory%20shortage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20elevated%20mortgage%20rates%20discourage%20homeowners%20from%20listing%20their%20properties%20for%20sale%20as%20many%20locked%20in%20lower%20borrowing%20costs%20in%20the%20last%20decade%20before%20Fed's%20tightening%20campaign.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20has%20the%20effect%20of%20propping%20up%20home%20prices%20even%20as%20demand%20stays%20low%20because%20of%20rising%20mortgage%20rates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20have%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fhousing-market-home-prices-frozen-mortgage-rates-interest-affordability-fed-2023-5%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520housing%2520market%2520is%2520frozen%252C%2520and%2520affordability%2520is%2520unlikely%2520to%2Ckeeps%2520an%2520eye%2520on%2520inflation.%5C%22%3Eaffordability%20is%20unlikely%20to%20improve%3C%2Fa%3E%20until%20mortgage%20rates%20pull%20back%20more%20significantly%2C%20which%20could%20encourage%20more%20buyers%20to%20enter%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYun%20doesn't%20necessarily%20think%20that's%20the%20case.%20Though%20home%20prices%20will%20stay%20elevated%20as%20mortgage%20rates%20see%20little%20change%2C%20household%20incomes%20rise%20by%20an%20average%204%25-5%25%20each%20year%2C%20Yun%20said%2C%20meaning%20a%20stagnant%20housing%20market%20will%20will%20give%20buyers%20time%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20the%20high%20costs%20of%20housing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it%20could%20take%20years%20for%20buyers%20to%20close%20the%20affordability%20gap%2C%20as%20higher-for-longer%20mortgage%20rates%20are%20the%20%26quot%3Bnew%20normal%26quot%3B%2C%20Yun%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20people%20are%20able%20to%20get%206%25%20%5Bmortgage%20rates%5D%2C%20they%20consider%20themselves%20as%20lucky.%20I%20think%20the%20new%20condition%20will%20be%20something%20around%206%25%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20in%20line%20with%20what%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fhousing-market-home-prices-frozen-mortgage-rates-interest-affordability-fed-2023-5%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520housing%2520market%2520is%2520frozen%252C%2520and%2520affordability%2520is%2520unlikely%2520to%2Ckeeps%2520an%2520eye%2520on%2520inflation.%5C%22%3Ereal%20estate%20experts%20see%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0through%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-recession-us-economy-mortgage-rates-home-prices-affordability-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689423300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F645f9fde11971c00188f3cbc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fhousing-market-recession-us-economy-mortgage-rates-home-prices-affordability-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Odds%20are%20rising%20that%20the%20US%20avoids%20a%20bad%20recession.%20That%20means%20homebuyers%20could%20be%20waiting%20even%20longer%20for%20their%20chance%20to%20break%20into%20the%20market.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jsor%40insider.com%20(Jennifer%20Sor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fhousing-market-recession-us-economy-mortgage-rates-home-prices-affordability-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Modi%20In%20France%20-%20Celebrating%20The%20Past%2C%20Preparing%20For%20The%20Future%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20moment%20of%20transformational%20change%20in%20the%20global%20order%2C%20with%20growing%20uncertainty%20about%20the%20future.%20To%20navigate%20this%20uncertain%20environment%2C%20new%20partnerships%20and%20new%20platforms%20are%20taking%20shape%20as%20nations%20struggle%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20the%20world%20around%20them.%20At%20a%20time%20like%20this%2C%20India%20has%20become%20the%20centre%20of%20attraction%20of%20the%20world.%20Today%2C%20all%20major%20powers%20of%20the%20world%20want%20to%20have%20a%20robust%20partnership%20with%20India.%20Indian%20diplomatic%20activity%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20busy%20calendar%20stand%20testimony%20to%20New%20Delhi's%20growing%20centrality%20in%20the%20emerging%20international%20milieu.%20Against%20this%20backdrop%2C%20after%20his%20successful%20state%20visit%20to%20America%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20was%20in%20France%20this%20week%20as%20the%20chief%20guest%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20the%20French%20national%20day%20-%20Bastille%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20visit%20was%20a%20celebration%20of%2025%20years%20of%20their%20bilateral%20strategic%20partnership%2C%20as%20Modi%20was%20conferred%20the%20Grand%20Cross%20of%20the%20Legion%20of%20Honour%20by%20Macron.%20A%20269-member%20Indian%20tri-services%20contingent%20participated%20in%20the%20Bastille%20Day%20parade%2C%20marching%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20'Saare%20jahan%20se%20achcha'%20and%20three%20Rafale%20fighter%20jets%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20joined%20the%20flypast%20along%20with%20French%20jets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERelations%20between%20India%20and%20France%20have%20stood%20the%20test%20of%20time%2C%20with%20France%20supporting%20India's%20stand%20on%20internationally%20disputed%20and%20divisive%20topics%20ranging%20from%20Kashmir%20to%20nuclear%20power.%20France%20was%20the%20first%20country%20with%20veto%20power%20to%20support%20India's%20permanent%20membership%20in%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council.%20The%20strategic%20partnership%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20gained%20momentum%20in%20the%20last%20decade%20of%20the%20last%20century.%20After%20the%20nuclear%20tests%2C%20when%20the%20wider%20West%20imposed%20sanctions%20on%20India%2C%20France%20did%20not%20join%20that%20bandwagon.%20The%20best%20thing%20about%20Indo-French%20relations%20is%20that%20both%20countries%20have%20shown%20a%20willingness%20to%20adapt%20this%20friendship%20to%20the%2021st%20century.%20The%20similar%20approach%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20President%20Macron%20on%20many%20global%20issues%20confirms%20this.%20Both%20leaders%20attach%20great%20importance%20to%20strategic%20autonomy%20in%20any%20partnership.%20Despite%20being%20a%20member%20of%20NATO%2C%20France%20showed%20the%20same%20practical%20attitude%20towards%20Russia%20as%20India%20did.%20France's%20often%20immediate%20support%20for%20important%20initiatives%20of%20India%20also%20shows%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20bilateral%20partnership.%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20personal%20bond%20with%20Macron%20remains%20an%20important%20factor%20in%20deepening%20relations%20with%20France%20at%20a%20time%20of%20great%20geopolitical%20turbulence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrance%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20key%20defence%20partner%20of%20India%2C%20and%20this%20partnership%20gained%20a%20new%20dimension%20during%20the%20visit%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20has%20forced%20India%20to%20reconsider%20its%20excessive%20strategic%20dependence%20on%20one%20nation.%20Therefore%2C%20India%20is%20focusing%20on%20expanding%20defence%20partnerships%20with%20key%20countries%20as%20well%20as%20becoming%20self-sufficient%20in%20defence%20production.%20In%20this%2C%20countries%20like%20France%20become%20vital%3B%20they%20are%20not%20only%20ready%20to%20provide%20state-of-the-art%20defence%20equipment%2C%20but%20also%20encourage%20co-production%20and%20co-development%20by%20sharing%20their%20technology.%20An%20MoU%20between%20Mazgon%20Dockyard%20Ltd%20and%20Naval%20Group%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20three%20additional%20submarines%20under%20the%20P75%20programme%20as%20well%20as%20a%20roadmap%20for%20cooperation%20in%20advanced%20aeronautical%20technologies%20by%20supporting%20the%20joint%20development%20of%20a%20combat%20aircraft%20engine%20between%20Safran%20and%20DRDO%20(Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation)%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20redefine%20the%20Indo-French%20defence%20partnership.%20India%20will%20be%20setting%20up%20a%20Technical%20Office%20of%20the%20DRDO%20at%20its%20Embassy%20in%20Paris%20to%20further%20accelerate%20the%20process%20of%20high-tech%20defence%20collaborations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indo-Pacific%20region%20is%20a%20geography%20of%20common%20concern%20to%20India%20and%20France%2C%20so%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20roadmap%20of%20India-France%20Cooperation%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20is%20likely%20to%20make%20this%20engagement%20more%20operational.%20Given%20the%20interests%20of%20both%20countries%20in%20this%20geography%2C%20they%20are%20also%20joining%20hands%20with%20other%20like-minded%20nations%20in%20carving%20new%20platforms.%20Where%20France%20is%20strengthening%20a%20front%20together%20with%20Australia%20and%20India%2C%20the%20trio%20of%20France%2C%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20and%20India%20are%20coming%20together%20considering%20their%20interests%20in%20the%20Arabian%20Sea.%20PM%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20the%20UAE%20while%20returning%20from%20France%20also%20has%20deep%20implications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20announced%20the%20launch%20of%20India's%20Unified%20Payment%20Interface%20(UPI)%20in%20France%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20five-year%20validity%20short-stay%20Schengen%20Visa%20for%20Indians%20who%20are%20degree%20holders%20from%20French%20educational%20institutions%20(Masters%20and%20above).%20The%20mobility%20of%20skilled%20professionals%20is%20now%20emerging%20as%20a%20key%20aspect%20of%20India's%20engagement%20with%20the%20wider%20West.%20France's%20decision%20to%20expand%20the%20scope%20of%20visas%20for%20Indian%20students%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20European%20nations%20are%20vying%20with%20countries%20like%20Australia%20and%20Canada%20to%20attract%20numerous%20students%20going%20abroad%20to%20study.%20From%20blue%20economy%20and%20ocean%20governance%20to%20renewable%20energy%2C%20Artificial%20Intelligence%2C%20semiconductors%20and%20digital%20technology%2C%20the%20ambit%20of%20issues%20is%20widening%20for%20India%20and%20France%20to%20work%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20met%20French%20business%20leaders%20and%20invited%20them%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20India's%20growth%20story.%20The%20dynamism%20of%20the%20Indian%20economy%20is%20now%20luring%20global%20corporate%20giants%20to%20India.%20In%20recent%20times%2C%20India%20has%20moved%20forward%20with%20Free%20Trade%20Agreements%20(FTAs)%20with%20various%20nations.%20The%20European%20Union%20is%20also%20keen%20to%20finally%20gain%20some%20traction%20on%20its%20long-pending%20FTA%20with%20India.%20The%20French%20leadership%20will%20be%20crucial%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20India%20and%20France%20celebrate%2025%20years%20of%20their%20strategic%20partnership%2C%20Modi's%20visit%20has%20prepared%20the%20framework%20of%20this%20relationship%20for%20the%20next%2025%20years.%20The%20political%20comfort%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20is%20opening%20up%20new%20avenues%20of%20cooperation%20for%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Paris%2C%20which%20the%20political%20leadership%20seems%20more%20than%20willing%20to%20embrace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHarsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20He%20is%20Vice%20President%20-%20Studies%20and%20Foreign%20Policy%20at%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20He%20is%20also%20Director%20(Honorary)%20of%20Delhi%20School%20of%20Transnational%20Affairs%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689422940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fcq7enrbg_modi-macron_650x400_14_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmodi-in-france-celebrating-the-past-preparing-for-the-future-4210412%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20visit%20was%20a%20celebration%20of%2025%20years%20of%20their%20bilateral%20strategic%20partnership%2C%20as%20Modi%20was%20conferred%20the%20Grand%20Cross%20of%20the%20Legion%20of%20Honour%20by%20Macron.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv