esidences%20-%20was%20claimed%20by%20the%20wronged%20and%20angry%20Yamuna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENothing%20unusual%20about%20the%20event%2C%20as%20India%20has%20a%20tradition%20of%20bad%20civic%20management%20across%20most%20states%2C%20and%20we%20are%20inured%20to%20flooding%2C%20traffic%20pileups%2C%20haphazard%20and%20dangerous%20constructions%2C%20and%20disappearing%20forests.%20Only%20this%20time%2C%20it%20is%20the%20national%20capital's%20wealthiest%20that%20were%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legend%20has%20it%20that%20an%20elderly%20guard%20from%20the%20'Marghat%20Wale%20Hanuman%20Baba'%20temple%20came%20shouting%20to%20the%20posh%20side%20of%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20Road%20aka%20Ring%20Road%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%2013%20July%2C%20warning%20that%20the%20water%20level%20was%20rising.%20He%20was%20promptly%20shooed%20away%20as%20a%20drunkard%20by%20the%20posh%20guards%20of%20posh%20people.%20By%207%20am%2C%20the%20cars%20parked%20on%20Bela%20Road%20began%20to%20float.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20noon%2C%20these%20cars%20attained%20celebrity.%20The%20national%20media%20launched%20its%20warriors%20in%20chest-deep%20water%20to%20bring%20ground%20reports.%20My%20husband%20tweeted%20that%20it%20was%20a%20red-letter%20day%20in%20the%20life%20of%20his%20car.%20And%20that's%20when%20it%20dawned%20upon%20all%20of%20us.%20Among%20the%20fancy%2C%20expensive%20cars%20floating%20around%20in%20Civil%20Lines%2C%20our%20Maruti%20-a%20decades-old%20symbol%20of%20middle-classness%20-%20was%20trying%20to%20act%20normal.%20Imagine%20Kangana%20Ranaut's%20Rani%20in%20%3Cem%3EQueen%3C%2Fem%3E%20suddenly%20swimming%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Great%20Gatsby%3C%2Fem%3E%20partygoers%20on%20a%20yacht%20in%20Miami.%20There's%20a%20Mercedes%20on%20the%20left%20and%20a%20Landcruiser%20on%20the%20right%2C%20our%20humble%20and%20hardworking%20Baleno%20trying%20to%20hold%20its%20head%20high%20in%20the%20middle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOur%20flooded%20street%20and%20if%20you%20look%20very%20carefully%20my%20flooded%20car%20makes%20a%20cameo%20appearance%20in%20this%20stellar%20%E2%81%A6%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fndtv%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ndtv%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%81%A9%20report.%20No%20electricity%20or%20water%2C%20so%205%20seconds%20of%20fame%20will%20have%20to%20do...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F1UzgePmxM3%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F1UzgePmxM3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Praveen%20Swami%20(%40praveenswami)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpraveenswami%2Fstatus%2F1679404613550702593%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20tweeted%20the%20photo%20of%20this%20submerged%20social%20warrior%20later%20that%20afternoon.%20The%20caption%20started%20WWIII%20in%20my%20mentions.%20The%20followers%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20descended%20in%20full%20force%20to%20defend%20the%20honour%20of%20their%20leaders.%20There%20was%20an%20occasional%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20fan%2C%20trying%20to%20clutch%20at%20the%20straws%20of%20relevance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOne%20of%20my%20cars%20decided%20to%20go%20for%20a%20swim%20today.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThank%20you%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40narendramodi%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThank%20you%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FArvindKejriwal%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ArvindKejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFor%20giving%20us%20this%20free-access%20swimming%20pool%20in%20the%20most%20VIP%20Area%20of%20Delhi.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FDelhiFloods%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23DelhiFloods%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Fdelhiflood%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23delhiflood%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FS9f0uB8EYU%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FS9f0uB8EYU%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Nishtha%20Gautam%20(%40TedhiLakeer)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTedhiLakeer%2Fstatus%2F1679438053939777537%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20zealots%2C%20however%2C%20pointed%20out%20'elitism'%20in%20the%20tweet%2C%20confirming%20my%20long-held%20belief%20that%20the%20most%20obnoxious%20people%20usually%20are%20those%20that%20lack%20a%20sense%20of%20humour.%20The%20summary%20of%20countless%20replies%20is%20the%20following%3A%20Good%20that%20your%20car%20drowned%2C%20you%20entitled%20b*%24%26amp%3B*!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20here%20is%20the%20thing%20-%20when%20Delhi's%20'VIP'%20area%20was%20flooded%2C%20the%20biggest%20talking%20point%20was%20not%20about%20the%20damage%20its%20residents%20faced.%20It%20was%20the%20realisation%20that%20this%20neighbourhood%20was%20inundated%20despite%20some%20of%20the%20strictest%20floor%20area%20ratio%20regulations%2C%20the%20quick%20reaction%20of%20civic%20authorities%20(because%20everyone%20important%20knows%20someone%20more%20important)%2C%20and%20the%20constant%20gaze%20of%20national%20media.%20Imagine%20the%20horror%20unleashed%20on%20those%20who%20live%20in%20areas%20that%20can%20boast%20of%20none%20of%20the%20above.%20Actually%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20left%20to%20the%20imagination%20anymore.%20It's%20for%20everyone%20to%20see.%20If%20at%20all%2C%20this%20imagination%20hardly%20ever%20translates%20into%20action%20that%20averts%20the%20next%20disaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20rather%20weak%20argument%20going%20around%20about%20the%20inevitability%20of%20natural%20disasters.%20It's%20the%20biggest%20con%20-%20to%20lull%20us%20into%20the%20comfort%20of%20calm%20resignation.%20The%20meme-like%20%26quot%3BAb%20kya%20hi%20kar%20sakte%20hain%26quot%3B%20attitude.%20Year%20after%20year%2C%20a%20chain%20of%20drought%20and%20deluge%20shackles%20India's%20cities%20and%20villages.%20We%20are%20rarely%20prepared%20for%20either.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20often%20mistake%20one%20for%20the%20other.%20A%20senior%20police%20officer%20tells%20me%20that%20he%20was%20busy%20preparing%20plans%20to%20save%20people%20from%20starvation%20till%20last%20month%20because%202023%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20drought%20year%2C%20thanks%20to%20met%20department%20predictions.%20Silt%20kept%20getting%20deposited%20on%20the%20bed%20of%20the%20Yamuna%2C%20elevating%20it%20by%2010-15%20feet%20without%20the%20extra%20water%2C%20and%20nobody%20cared.%20Delhi's%20drainage%20system%20has%20stayed%20clogged%20for%20decades.%20Yamuna%20floodplains%20have%20been%20badly%20encroached%20upon%20by%20the%20rich%20and%20the%20poor%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20Twitter%20trolls%20who%20got%20a%20kick%20out%20of%20serenading%20the%20socialist%20nature%20of%20Nature%2C%20my%20tuppence%20is%3A%20Who%20are%20you%20kidding%2C%20bunny%3F%20It%20may%20be%20the%20cheapest%20car%20in%20Civil%20Lines%2C%20but%20the%20Blue%20Baleno%20is%20fully%20insured.%20(Because%20my%20husband%20is%20the%20most%20efficient%20man%20in%20the%20world.)%20Yes%2C%20you%20guessed%20it%20right%2C%20he%20forced%20me%20to%20insert%20the%20parenthesis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20financial%20damage%20caused%20by%20the%20historic%20Delhi%20floods%20to%20our%20property%20won't%20bankrupt%20us%20in%20Civil%20Lines.%20We'll%20go%20back%20to%20our%20everyday%20lives%20once%20electricity%20is%20back.%20Till%20then%2C%20we%20have%20our%20friends%2C%20family%2C%20and%20five-star%20hotels%20to%20take%20us%20in.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20question%20of%20survival%20but%20comfort%20for%20us%20here.%20The%20only%20issue%20here%20is%20the%20absolute%20brokenness%20of%20our%20country's%20systems.%20T