E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20as%20East%20Asia%2C%20including%20countries%20like%20Japan%2C%20Korea%20and%20China%2C%20witnessed%20significant%20growth%2075%20years%20ago%2C%20it%20is%20now%20India%E2%80%99s%20turn%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wickremesinghe%20said%2C%20while%20addressing%20the%20Indian%20CEO%20Forum%20in%20Colombo%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20makes%20no%20difference%20to%20us%20if%20India%20(the%20Indian%20rupee)%20becomes%20a%20common%20currency.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20go%20about%20it.%20We%20must%20become%20more%20open%20to%20the%20outside%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20president%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20world%20is%20evolving%20and%20India%20is%20undergoing%20rapid%20development%2C%20particularly%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20leadership%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20Sri%20Lanka%20benefits%20from%20its%20proximity%20to%20India%2C%20coupled%20with%20a%20rich%20history%2C%20cultural%20heritage%20and%20longstanding%20trading%20relationships%20spanning%202%2C500%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tackle%20its%20economic%20crisis%2C%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Finternational%2Findia-provided-nearly-4-billion-in-food-financial-assistance-to-sri-lanka-122090500038_1.html%5C%22%3Ehad%20provided%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20island%20nation%20an%20assistance%20package%20of%20%244%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fexplainer-rbi-rupee-settlement-international-trade%5C%22%3EExplainer%3A%20How%20Feasible%20Is%20Rbi%E2%80%99s%20Push%20to%20Settle%20International%20Trade%20in%20Rupees%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Feconomy%2Findia-offers-rupee-trade-option-to-nations-facing-dollar-crunch%2Famp-11680307499492.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20India%20will%20offer%20its%20currency%20as%20an%20alternative%20for%20trade%20to%20countries%20that%20are%20facing%20a%20shortage%20of%20dollars.%20The%20move%20was%20announced%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20sharpest%20tightening%20in%20monetary%20policy%20by%20the%20US%20Federal%20Reserve%20in%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20allowed%2018%20countries%20to%20open%20Special%20Vostro%20Rupee%20Accounts%20for%20settling%20payments%20in%20Indian%20rupees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India%20is%20attempting%20to%20internationalise%20the%20rupee%2C%20and%20many%20countries%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Feconomy%2Fabout-35-countries-show-interest-in-rupee-trade-mechanism%2F2904948%2F%5C%22%3Ehave%20expressed%20interest%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20understanding%20the%20rupee%20trade%20mechanism%2C%20it%20is%20still%20to%20be%20seen%20how%20much%20global%20trade%20is%20happening%20in%20rupees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.orfonline.org%2Fexpert-speak%2Frupee-going-global-acceptable-for-south-asia%2F%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20through%20bilateral%20agreements%2C%20the%20Indian%20rupee%20is%20an%20accepted%20currency%20in%20neighbouring%20Nepal%20and%20Bhutan%2C%20but%20these%20nations%20cannot%20use%20it%20for%20trading%20with%20a%20third%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20a%20government%20official%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Findian-refiners-start-paying-for-oil-imports-in-yuan-report%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20Reuters%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Frussias-huge-rupee-reserves-due-to-defence-deals-official%5C%22%3Eaccumulation%20of%20the%20rupee%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20%E2%80%98not%20desirable%E2%80%99%20for%20Russia.%20Therefore%2C%20Indian%20refiners%2C%20inc