o%20caught%20on%20camera%20from%20a%20plane%20window%20that%20was%20flying%20from%20Chennai%20to%20Dhaka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20was%20shared%20on%20Twitter%20by%20Dr%20P%20V%20Venkitakrishnan%2C%20Director%20(retired)%2C%20ISRO%20Materials%2C%20and%20Rocket%20Manufacturing%20Expert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20captioned%20the%20visuals%20as%2C%20%26quot%3BLaunch%20of%20Chandrayan%203%20from%20Flight.%26quot%3B%20Sometime%20after%20takeoff%20from%20the%20Chennai%20to%20Dhaka%20flight%2C%20the%20pilot%20announced%2C%20Watch%20this%20historical%20event.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ELaunch%20of%20Chandrayan%203%20from%20flight.%20Sometime%20after%20takeoff%20from%20Chennai%20to%20Dhaka%20flight%2C%20pilot%20announced%20to%20watch%20this%20historical%20event%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FKpf39iciRD%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FKpf39iciRD%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Dr.%20P%20V%20Venkitakrishnan%20(%40DrPVVenkitakri1)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrPVVenkitakri1%2Fstatus%2F1680066898015424514%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20shared%2C%20the%20video%20has%20received%20lakhs%20of%20views%20and%20countless%20likes%2C%20leaving%20many%20internet%20users%20speechless%20by%20the%20passenger's%20photographic%20prowess.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20journey%20from%20Earth%20to%20the%20moon%20for%20Chandrayaan-3%20is%20estimated%20to%20take%20about%20a%20month%2C%20and%20the%20landing%20is%20expected%20on%20August%2023.%20Upon%20landing%2C%20it%20will%20operate%20for%20one%20lunar%20day%2C%20which%20is%20approximately%2014%20Earth%20days.%20One%20day%20on%20the%20Moon%20is%20equal%20to%2014%20days%20on%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%2C%20India's%20third%20lunar%20exploration%20mission%2C%20will%20make%20India%20the%20fourth%20country%20after%20the%20US%2C%20China%2C%20and%20Russia%20to%20land%20its%20spacecraft%20on%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20moon%20and%20demonstrate%20the%20country's%20abilities%20for%20a%20safe%20and%20soft%20landing%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%20is%20the%20ISRO's%20follow-up%20attempt%20after%20the%20Chandrayaan-2%20mission%20faced%20challenges%20during%20its%20soft%20landing%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface%20in%202019%20and%20was%20eventually%20deemed%20to%20have%20failed%20its%20core%20mission%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%20will%20be%20inserted%20into%20the%20Lunar%20Transfer%20Trajectory%20after%20the%20orbit-raising%20manoeuvres.%20Covering%20a%20distance%20of%20over%20300%2C000%20km%2C%20it%20will%20reach%20the%20Moon%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks.%20Scientific%20instruments%20will%20study%20the%20Moon's%20surface%20and%20enhance%20our%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%20is%20equipped%20with%20a%20lander%2C%20a%20rover%2C%20and%20a%20propulsion%20module.%20It%20weighs%20around%203%2C900%20kilogrammes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20the%20agency)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689420960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F7qeksru8_chandrayaan-3s-launch-view-from-flight_625x300_15_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fchandrayaan-3-lift-off-recorded-from-plane-window-spectacular-video-goes-viral-4210318%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20a%20flight%20between%20Chennai%20and%20Dhaka%2C%20a%20passenger%20with%20a%20window%20seat%20had%20the%20good%20fortune%20to%20shoot%20the%20launch%20of%20ISRO's%20Chandrayaan-3.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fchandrayaan-3-lift-off-recorded-from-plane-window-spectacular-video-goes-viral-4210318%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fchandrayaan-3-lift-off-recorded-from-plane-window-spectacular-video-goes-viral-4210318%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fchandrayaan-3-lift-off-recorded-from-plane-window-spectacular-video-goes-viral-4210318%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi%20Goes%20To%20Supreme%20Court%20For%20Relief%20In%20%5C%22Modi%20Surname%5C%22%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Congress%20president%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20today%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20challenging%20the%20Gujarat%20High%20Court's%20refusal%20to%20stay%20his%20conviction%20in%20the%20criminal%20defamation%20case%20over%20his%20'Modi%20surname'%20remark%2C%20which%20led%20to%20his%20disqualification%20as%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20was%20disqualified%20as%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20on%20March%2024%2C%202023%20after%20a%20Gujarat%20court%20convicted%20him%20and%20sentenced%20him%20to%20two-years%20in%20jail%20on%20charges%20of%20criminal%20defamation%20for%20his%20%26quot%3BHow%20come%20all%20thieves%20have%20Modi%20as%20the%20common%20surname%3F%26quot%3B%20remark%20made%20during%20an%20election%20rally%20at%20Kolar%20in%20Karnataka%20on%20April%2013%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20stay%20on%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20conviction%20could%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20his%20reinstatement%20as%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP.%20However%2C%20he%20has%20not%20received%20any%20relief%20from%20either%20the%20sessions%20court%20or%20the%20Gujarat%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complainant%2C%20BJP%20MLA%20Purnesh%20Modi%2C%20had%20earlier%20filed%20a%20caveat%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20that%20he%20be%20heard%20if%20the%20Congress%20leader%20moves%20a%20plea%20challenging%20the%20high%20court%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20had%20dismissed%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20appeal%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20now%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour%20to%20have%20purity%20in%20politics%26quot%3B.%20It%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20people%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Bmen%20of%20clear%20antecedent%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20a%20stay%20on%20conviction%20is%20not%20a%20rule%2C%20but%20an%20exception%20resorted%20to%20only%20in%20rare%20cases%20and%20there%20was%20no%20reasonable%20ground%20to%20stay%20his%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20is%20seeking%20a%20stay%20on%20conviction%20on%20absolutely%20non-existent%20grounds%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20added%2C%20observing%20that%20refusal%20to%20stay%20the%20conviction%20would%20not%20in%20any%20way%20result%20in%20injustice%20to%20the%20applicant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E53-year-old%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20elected%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20Wayanad%20in%20Kerala%20in%202019%2C%20was%20disqualified%20as%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%20after%20a%20metropolitan%20magistrate's%20court%20in%20Surat%20sentenced%20him%20to%20two%20years%20in%20jail%20after%20convicting%20him%20under%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%20sections%20499%20and%20500%20(criminal%20defamation).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2010%20cases%20pending%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20A%20complaint%20has%20also%20been%20filed%20against%20him%20by%20the%20grandson%20of%20Veer%20Savarkar%20in%20Pune%20Court%20after%20Gandhi%20used%20terms%20against%20Veer%20Savarkar%20at%20Cambridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689420720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fdbhmgm5g_rahul-gandhi-afp_625x300_02_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-files-petition-in-supreme-court-over-gujarat-high-courts-refusal-to-stay-his-conviction-in-defamation-case-4210280%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Congress%20president%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20today%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20challenging%20the%20Gujarat%20High%20Cou