20Cat%20Park%2C%20north%20of%20Paphos%2C%20Cyprus.%3Cp%3ESally%20Hayden%2FSOPA%20Images%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAn%20outbreak%20of%20feline%20coronavirus%20is%20killing%20off%20cats%20on%20a%20Mediterranean%20island%20known%20for%20its%20strays.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESome%20300%2C000%20are%20estimated%20to%20have%20died%20since%20January.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20feline%20medicine%20specialist%20said%20that%20its%20scale%20%26quot%3Bhas%20never%20been%20seen%20in%20living%20or%20reported%20history.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECoronavirus%20is%20wreaking%20havoc%20on%20cat%20populations%20in%20Cyprus%20as%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20have%20died%20since%20January%20in%20what%20could%20be%20the%20largest-ever%20outbreak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStray%20cats%20are%20an%20iconic%20feature%20of%20many%20parts%20of%20Southern%20Europe%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%20They%20lounge%20on%20walls%2C%20soak%20up%20the%20sun%20in%20the%20street%2C%20and%20sit%20on%20outdoor%20tables.%20In%20Cyprus%2C%20it%20is%20estimated%20that%20there%20are%20as%20many%20cats%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Flifestyle%2Foddly-enough%2Fdespite-ancient-cat-connections-cyprus-is-swamped-with-strays-2021-06-24%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20there%20are%20humans%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20it%20issometimes%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ciprusiingatlanok.hu%2Fen%2Finformations-about-cyprus%2Fcyprus-is-an-island-of-cats%2F82%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAccording%2520to%2520legends%252C%2520this%2520is%2Cand%2520not%2520without%2520any%2520foundation.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E'island%20of%20cats.'%3C%2Fa%3E%20It%20is%20said%20that%20felines%20were%20brought%20to%20the%20island%20to%20hunt%20venomous%20snakes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20300%2C000%20have%20died%20after%20a%20coronavirus%20outbreak%20that%20causes%20feline%20infectious%20peritonitis%20(FIP)%2C%20per%20media%20reports%20quoting%20Dinos%20Ayiomamitis%20of%20animal%20rights%20groups%20Cat%20Paws%20Cyprus%20and%20Cyprus%20Voice%20for%20Animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFIP%20symptoms%20include%20fever%2C%20abdominal%20swelling%2C%20and%20going%20off%20food.%20It%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vet.cornell.edu%2Fdepartments-centers-and-institutes%2Fcornell-feline-health-center%2Fhealth-information%2Ffeline-health-topics%2Ffeline-infectious-peritonitis%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFeline%2520infectious%2520peritonitis%2520(FIP)%2520is%2Cfeline%2520enteric%2520coronavirus%2520(FeCV).%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealmost%20always%20fatal%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20treatment%2C%20according%20to%20Cornell%20University.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can't%20be%20spread%20to%20humans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221777%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20domestic%20cat%20suffering%20from%20Feline%20Infectious%20Peritonitis%20(FIP)%20is%20in%20quarantine%20at%20a%20veterinary%20clinic%20in%20Nicosia%20on%20June%2020%2C%202023.%20A%20new%20strain%20of%20feline%20coronavirus%2C%20Feline%20infectious%20peritonitis%20(FIP)%20--%20which%20is%20not%20transmittable%20to%20humans%20--%20is%20wreaking%20havoc%20on%20the%20prolific%20cat%20population%20of%20Cyprus.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b2770af9a25900194771eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20domestic%20cat%20in%20quarantine%20at%20a%20veterinary%20clinic%20in%20Nicosia%20on%20June%2020%2C%202023.%20A%20new%20strain%20of%20feline%20coronavirus%2C%20Feline%20infectious%20peritonitis%20(FIP)%20--%20which%20is%20not%20transmittable%20to%20humans%20--%20is%20wreaking%20havoc%20on%20the%20cat%20population%20of%20Cyprus%2C%20known%20by%20some%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bisland%20of%20cats.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20CHRISTINA%20ASSI%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20107%20cases%20have%20officially%20been%20recorded%2C%20but%20Ayiomamitis%20argued%20the%20real%20number%20is%20much%20higher.%20His%20calculation%20is%20based%20on%20an%20estimated%2020%25%20to%2030%25%20mortality%20rate%20among%20Cyprus'%20one%20million%20cats%2C%20many%20of%20them%20strays%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.channel4.com%2Fnews%2Ffactcheck%2Ffactcheck-how-many-cats-have-died-of-feline-coronavirus-in-cyprus-and-are-there-uk-cases%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Channel%204%20FactCheck%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outbreak%20%26quot%3Bstarted%20in%20the%20capital%20city%20of%20Nicosia%20in%20January%20and%20spread%20throughout%20the%20whole%20island%20within%20three%20to%20four%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20Demetris%20Epaminondas%2C%20vice-president%20of%20the%20Pancyprian%20Veterinary%20Association%2C%20told%20the%20Daily%20Mail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221777%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Veterinarian%20Kostis%20Larkou%20tends%20to%20a%20cat%20suffering%20from%20Feline%20Infectious%20Peritonitis%20(FIP)%2C%20at%20clinic%20in%20Nicosia%20on%20June%2020%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b2778ef9a25900194771f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVeterinarian%20Kostis%20Larkou%20tends%20to%20a%20cat%20suffering%20from%20Feline%20Infectious%20Peritonitis%20(FIP)%2C%20at%20clinic%20in%20Nicosia%20on%20June%2020%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20CHRISTINA%20ASSI%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20scale%20%26quot%3Bhas%20never%20been%20seen%20in%20living%20or%20reported%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20Dani%C3%A8lle%20Gunn-Moore%2C%20a%20feline%20medicine%20specialist%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Edinburgh%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fglobal-health%2Fscience-and-disease%2Fcyprus-dead-cat-island-feline-coronavirus-outbreak%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20Telegraph%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20said%20that%20there%20had%20been%20a%20rise%20in%20reports%20of%20dead%20cats%20in%20the%20streets%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGunn-Moore%20added%20that%20it%20could%20mean%20a%20stronger%20strain%20of%20FIP%20is%20circulating%20and%20pointed%20to%20anecdotal%20evidence%20of%20outbreaks%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20Turkey%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bpotentially%26quot%3B%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDomesticated%20cats%20are%20being%20held%20at%20clinics%20to%20avoid%20infection%2C%20the%20Daily%20Mail%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECyprus'%20relationship%20with%20cats%20goes%20back%20to%20the%20early%20days%20of%20human%20history.%20Bones%20of%20domesticated%20cats%20have%20been%20found%20near%20human%20graves%20that%20date%20back%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fthe-cat-sat-on-a-cyprus-mat-9500-years-ago-vcwgjtgwbnk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E7%2C000%20to%207%2C500%20BC.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0A%20monastery%20on%20Cyprus%20is%20dedicated%20to%20'St.%20Nicholas%20of%20the%20Cats'%20was%20once%20said%20to%20have%20two%20bells%3B%20one%20to%20people%20call%20to%20prayer%20and%20a%20second%20to%20call%20the%20cats%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Flifestyle%2Foddly-enough%2Fdespite-ancient-cat-connections-cyprus-is-swamped-with-strays-2021-06-24%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20Reuters.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdead-cats-lying-covid-kills-300000-felines-mediterranean-island-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689419968000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b2762c9751e300192a39ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bu