%20the%20future%20roadmap%20of%20ties.%20This%20MoU%20had%20been%20mentioned%20in%20an%20earlier%20version%20of%20the%20uploaded%20text.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOfficial%20sources%20claimed%20that%20the%20previous%20document%20was%20not%20the%20approved%20text%20and%20%E2%80%9Csome%20earlier%20negotiating%20text%20got%20uploaded.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fdefence-ties-serve-as-the-basic-pillar-of-india-france-bilateral-relations-modi%5C%22%3Eabsence%20of%20any%20Rafale%20jet%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20roadmap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20delegation-level%20talks%20between%20Indian%20and%20French%20leaders%20in%20Paris%20on%20Friday%2C%20July%2014%2C%20a%20slew%20of%20diplomatic%20documents%20were%20issued%20by%20both%20sides.%20The%20joint%20communique%20was%20a%20short%20text%2C%20with%20the%20substantial%20document%20being%20the%20%E2%80%98Horizon%202047%20%E2%80%93%2025th%20Anniversary%20of%20the%20India-France%20Strategic%20Partnership%2C%20Towards%20A%20Century%20of%20India-France%20Relations%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBased%20on%20the%20uploaded%20Horizon%202047%20document%20on%20the%20MEA%E2%80%99s%20website%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20other%20Indian%20media%20outlets%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fdefence-ties-serve-as-the-basic-pillar-of-india-france-bilateral-relations-modi%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported%20that%20there%20was%20an%20absence%20of%20the%20expected%20deal%20for%20purchasing%2026%20additional%20Rafale%20fighter%20jets%20for%20the%20Indian%20Navy.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%2C%20the%20text%20also%20had%20mentioned%20that%20India%20and%20France%20%E2%80%9Cwelcome%20the%20MoU%20between%20Mazgon%20Dockyard%20Ltd%20and%20Naval%20Group%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20three%20additional%20submarines%20under%20the%20P75%20programme%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20the%20deals%20had%20been%20approved%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20Defence%20Acquisition%20Council%20and%20announced%20by%20the%20Indian%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20on%20his%20Twitter%20account%20a%20day%20earlier%20on%20Thursday.%20While%20the%20price%20was%20still%20to%20be%20negotiated%2C%20the%20total%20cost%20of%20both%20the%20deals%20was%20estimated%20around%20%249.5%20billion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20on%20Saturday%20morning%2C%20India%20time%2C%20the%20line%20about%20the%20MoU%20for%20the%20three%20additional%20submarines%20had%20disappeared.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwebcache.googleusercontent.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dcache%3Ahttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fbilateral-documents.htm%3Fdtl%2F36806%2FHorizon_2047_25th_Anniversary_of_the_IndiaFrance_Strategic_Partnership_Towards_A_Century_of_IndiaFrance_Relations%26sxsrf%3DAB5stBjcMGapLWK7Gy_VnU3IFmF6pTHO0Q%3A1689419641736%26source%3Dhp%26ei%3DeX-yZLSpKpjt2roPuP6KmAI%26iflsig%3DAD69kcEAAAAAZLKNiRQ-nM0jl-o3mQOhmtr3TVeUGcST%26ved%3D0ahUKEwj0yfrMypCAAxWYtlYBHTi_AiMQ4dUDCAk%26uact%3D5%26oq%3Dcache%3Ahttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fbilateral-documents.htm%3Fdtl%2F36806%2FHorizon_2047_25th_Anniversary_of_the_IndiaFrance_Strategic_Partnership_Towards_A_Century_of_IndiaFrance_Relations%26gs_lp%%26sclient%3Dgws-wiz%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20cached%20version%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20earlier%20uploaded%20text%20shows%20the%20difference.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15164046%2FScreenshot-2023-07-15-at-4.39.34-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15164046%2FScreenshot-2023-07-15-at-4.39.34-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15164046%2FScreenshot-2023-07-15-at-4.39.34-PM-300x73.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15164046%2FScreenshot-2023-07-15-at-4.39.34-PM-1024x250.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663368%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22293%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAbove%2C%20the%20earlier%20version%20of%20the%20text.%20Below%20is%20the%20latest%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESources%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20an%20earlier%20text%20from%20the%20negotiation%20stage%20got%20uploaded%20on%20the%20MEA%20website%20for%20a%20short%20period%20of%20time%20and%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20the%20agreed%20upon%20text%2C%20in%20any%20way%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20sources%20added%20that%20the%20approved%20text%20now%20on%20the%20website%20is%20also%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elysee.fr%2Fadmin%2Fupload%2Fdefault%2F0001%2F15%2F13ca1dc3c8938ae4ce52f5c53e149ddd251099cb.pdf%5C%22%3Esame%20one%20published%20by%20the%20French%20government.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20change%20made%20in%20the%20current%20version%20is%20the%20deletion%20of%20the%20deadline%20to%20prepare%20a%20roadmap%20for%20joint%20development%20of%20a%20combat%20aircraft%20engine%20%E2%80%93%20originally%20scheduled%20to%20be%20finalised%20before%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year.%20The%20proposal%20for%20joint%20development%20remains%2C%20but%20this%20line%20has%20been%20removed%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CA%20roadmap%20on%20this%20project%20will%20be%20prepared%20between%20Safran%20and%20DRDO%20before%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20still%20not%20clear%20why%20the%20two%20deals%20are%20not%20part%20of%20deliverables%20when%20India%E2%80%99s%20DAC%20had%20initially%20green%20lit%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20question%20especially%20arises%20considering%20that%20the%20initial%20draft%20text%20did%20have%20the%20new%20Scorpene%20submarine%20deal%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20later%20taken%20out%20in%20the%20approved%20text%2C%20as%20sources%20had%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dassault-aviation.com%2Fen%2Fgroup%2Fpress%2Fpress-kits%2Findia-selects-the-navy-rafale%2F%5C%22%3EDassault%20Aviation%20issued%20a%20press%20release%20after%20the%20release%20of%20the%202047%20roadmap%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20stating%20that%20India%20has%20announced%20that%20it%20had%20chosen%20the%20Rafale%20fighter%20jets%20for%20the%20Indian%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20press%20briefing%20after%20the%20talks%2C%20the%20foreign%20secretary%20Vinay%20Kwatra%20had%20been%20questioned%20by%20reporters%20on%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20Rafale%20fighter%20jet%20deals%20in%20any%20of%20the%20diplomatic%20documents%2C%20especially%20the%20roadmap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20did%20not%20address%20this%20directly%2C%20but%20claimed%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9C2047%20Horizon%20document%20looks%20at%20security%20and%20sovereignty%20in%20a%20more%20holistic%20and%20a%20comprehensive%20manner%20rather%20than%20as%20a%20set%20of%20individual%20transactions%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20for%20that%20is%20because%20the%20metrics%20of%20defence%20partnership%20are%20not%20defined%20by%20a%20single%20acquisition%20or%20a%20non-acquisition%2C%20single%20procurement%20or%20a%20single%20transaction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said%2C%20on%20Friday%2C%20in%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20additional%20Rafale%20fighter%20jets%20deal%20was%20not%20mentioned%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20three%20Scorpene%20submarines%20line%20has%20been%20removed%20after%20publication%20%E2%80%93%20the%202047%20Horizon%20roadmap%20does%20mention%20other%20transactions%20like%20the%20one%20between%20HAL%20and%20Safran%20on%20the%20Shakti%20engine.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689417344000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15160435%2FScreenshot-2023-07-15-at-4.03.03.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fsubmarines-missing-india-france-accident-roadmap%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20comes%20after%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20Rafale%20jet%20deal%20in%20the%20roadmap.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fsubmarines-missing-india-france-accident-roadmap%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20'TMC%20Is%20Now%20Even%20Stronger%20in%20Bengal'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15175710%2FScreenshot-2023-07-15-at-5.39.18.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20of%20the%20Bengal%20Panchayat%20Elections%2C%20released%20by%20the%20State%20Election%20Commission%20(SEC)%2C%20spelt%20landslide%20victory%20for%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20Trinamool%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC%20won%20over%2034%2C000%20gram%20panchayat%20seats%2C%20while%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20managed%20to%20win%20only%20on%2010%2C000%20seats.%20The%20CPI(M)%20and%20Congress%20became%20the%20third%20and%20fourth%20parties%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20election%20results%20and%20their%20impact%20on%20Bengal%20politics%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20Kolkata-based%20political%20analyst%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20this%20election%20results%2C%20TMC%20looks%20much%20stronger%20than%20the%20BJP.%20I%20would%20question%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20claim%20of%20winning%2035%20seats%20in%20the%202024%20gener