ces%20in%20the%20UT%2C%20despite%20an%20almost%20five-year%20ban%20in%20place.%20This%20article%20will%20be%20update%20if%20we%20receive%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20RTI%20request%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EMinistry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20The%20Wire%20had%20asked%20for%20y%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eear-wise%20data%20on%20the%20number%20of%20individuals%20holding%20licensed%20guns%20in%20each%20state%20of%20the%20country.%20It%20had%20also%20asked%20for%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0categorisation%20of%20gun%20licences%2C%20such%20as%20licences%20for%20self-defence%2C%20professional%20requirements%2C%20sports%20shooting%2C%20etc.%2C%20and%20the%20number%20of%20licences%20issued%20in%20each%20category%2C%20state-wise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20response%20received%20only%20had%20data%20on%20gun%20licences%20issued%20in%20each%20state.%20It%20showed%20that%20as%20of%20June%2020%20this%20year%2C%20there%20were%2037.7%20lakh%20active%20gun%20licences%20across%20the%20country.%20This%20is%20over%204%20lakhs%20more%20than%20the%20licences%20that%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-has-33-69-lakh-gun-licences-uttar-pradesh-tops-list-with-12-77-lakh%2Fstory-uRQ9XGCy9wpczOiEMcFmAN.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eactive%20in%20December%202016%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20when%20data%20was%20last%20made%20publicly%20available.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENotably%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20the%20only%20Union%20Territory%20with%20a%20high%20number%20of%20gun%20license%20holders%20in%20the%20country%2C%20while%20Lakshadweep%20has%20zero%20licence%20holders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20following%20are%20the%20figures%20for%20gun%20licenses%20in%20other%20Union%20Territories%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%3Cstrong%3EUT%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%3Cstr