20on%20law%20and%20order%20situations.%20Then%20why%20the%20spike%20in%20gun%20licences%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%E2%80%99s%20latest%20data%2C%20UP%20reported%2036%2C363%20cases%20in%202021%20under%20the%20Arms%20Act%2C%201959.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtique%20Ahmed%2C%20a%20gangster%20and%20former%20politician%2C%20was%20recently%20shot%20at%2C%20along%20with%20his%20brother%20while%20in%20police%20custody.%20In%20its%20aftermath%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EPrint%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fsurge-in-gun-violence-gang-rivalry-related-murders-in-yogi-adityanaths-up-but-violent-crimes-on-decline%2F1526980%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20gu%3Cspan%3En-related%20violence%20in%20UP%20has%20increased%20since%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%2C%20reaching%20the%20highest%20level%20in%20India.%20NCRB%20data%20also%20reveals%20that%20UP%20ranks%20first%20in%20deaths%20due%20to%20accidental%20firing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPreviously%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20had%20held%20the%20top%20spot%20in%20cases%20registered%20under%20the%20Arms%20Act%2C%20but%20it%20has%20now%20fallen%20to%20second%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecently%2C%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Digvijaya%20Singh%20had%20accused%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20home%20minister%20Narottam%20Mishra%20of%20issuing%20gun%20licences%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20bribe%20of%20Rs%20five%20lakhs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20interview%20on%20%3Cem%3EThe%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FifjPa4sPiak%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ELallantop%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Mishra%20was%20asked%20about%20this%20allegation.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20process%20is%20transparent%20and%20if%20you%20have%20any%20evidence%20then%20show%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20countered.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RTI%20response%20received%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20shows%20that%20currently%20in%20MP%2C%20282%2C675%20people%20holds%20licences%2C%20which%20is%20a%2035%2C545%20hike%20over%20the%20figure%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E247%2C130%20available%20last%2C%20in%202016.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENagaland%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDarapuri%20%3Cspan%3Ealso%20points%20out%20how%20the%20case%20of%20Nagaland%20is%20significant.%20There%2C%2044%2C473%20individuals%20are%20authorised%20to%20carry%20weapons.%20He%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Nagaland%2C%20obtaining%20a%20licensed%20gun%20is%20easy%2C%20which%20explains%20the%20high%20number%20of%20state%20residents%20with%20gun%20licences.%20People%20from%20other%20states%20also%20get%20their%20licences%20approved%20through%20Nagaland.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202017%2C%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20also%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fpatna%2Fnow-arms-licence-seekers-from-state-head-to-nagaland%2Farticleshow%2F57967219.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20one%20can%20obtain%20a%20weapons%20licence%20in%20Nagaland%20within%20a%20month.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-gun-licenses-biren-singh-violence%3Futm%3Dauthorlistpage%5C%22%3EAlthough%20more%20licences%20were%20granted%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20overall%20Nagaland%20has%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20active%20gun%20licences%20in%20the%20northeast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20former%20Manipur%20police%20commissioner%20Raj%20Kumar%20Nimai