t-irans-anti-hijab-protests%5C%22%3EWatch%20%7C%20All%20You%20Need%20to%20Know%20About%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20Anti-hijab%20Protests%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20full%20statement%20is%20reproduced%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGeneva%20(July%205%2C%202023)%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIran%20must%20end%20its%20continuing%20crackdown%20on%20peaceful%20protesters%20and%20halt%20the%20wave%20of%20executions%2C%20mass%20arrests%20and%20detentions%20since%20the%20death%20in%20custody%20of%2022-year-old%20Jina%20Mahsa%20Amini%20last%20September.%20It%20must%20respect%2C%20fulfil%2C%20and%20protect%20the%20rights%20of%20all%20people%20in%20Iran%2C%20especially%20women%20and%20girls%2C%20the%20Independent%20International%20Fact-Finding%20Mission%20on%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Iran%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20first%20Oral%20Update%20to%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Council%2C%20the%20Fact-Finding%20Mission%20said%20the%20overall%20human%20rights%20situation%20in%20the%20country%20risks%20deteriorating%20further%20if%20no%20response%20is%20made%20to%20the%20concerns%20raised%20to%20date%20of%20alleged%20human%20rights%20violations%2C%20and%20if%20new%20legislation%2C%20which%20proposes%20harsher%20punishments%20on%20women%20and%20girls%20found%20in%20breach%20of%20forced%20veiling%20provisions%2C%20becomes%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJina%20Mahsa%E2%80%99s%20death%20in%20custody%20in%20September%2C%20following%20her%20arrest%20and%20detention%20by%20morality%20police%20for%20alleged%20non-observance%20of%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20law%20on%20forced%20veiling%2C%20sparked%20demonstrations%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTen%20months%20on%2C%20Jina%20Mahsa%E2%80%99s%20family%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20truth%20and%20justice%20remain%20unfulfilled%2C%20and%20we%20are%20concerned%20that%20domestic%20investigations%20have%20fallen%20short%20of%20international%20human%20rights%20norms%20and%20standards%2C%20including%20the%20requirements%20of%20promptness%2C%20independence%2C%20and%20transparency%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sara%20Hossain%2C%20the%20Chair%20of%20the%20FFM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Fact-Finding%20Mission%20highlighted%20several%20key%20areas%20of%20concerns.%20It%20drew%20attention%20to%20specific%20risks%20of%20further%20deterioration%20of%20the%20human%20rights%20of%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20protests%2C%20including%20lawyers%2C%20journalists%20and%20human%20rights%20defenders%2C%20and%20in%20particular%20women%20and%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllegations%20of%20human%20rights%20violations%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20protests%20are%20continuing%20to%20be%20heard%2C%20received%2C%20and%20investigated%20by%20the%20FFM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20of%20Iran%20announced%20that%2022%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20pardoned%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20protests.%20Our%20understanding%20is%20that%20these%20individuals%20were%20reportedly%20compelled%20to%20%E2%80%9Cexpress%20remorse%E2%80%9D%20thus%20to%20effectively%20admit%20guilt%20while%20also%20making%20a%20pledge%20not%20to%20commit%20%E2%80%9Csimilar%20crimes%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20future%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20their%20human%20rights%20including%20their%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20today%2C%20ten%20months%20after%20the%20events%2C%20no%20official%20data%20is%20publicly%20available%20regarding%20those%20arrested%2C%20detained%2C%20charged%20or%20convicted%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20protests.%20But%20reports%20continue%20to%20emerge%20of%20arrests%20and%20detentions%20of%20protesters%2C%20including%20women%20and%20girls%20refusing%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20forced%20veiling%20law%2C%20and%20of%20harassment%20of%20their%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20concerned%20by%20the%20continuous%20detention%20of%20human%20rights%20defenders%20and%20lawyers%20defending%20the%20protestors%20and%20at%20least%2017%20journalists%2C%20including%20Nilufar%20Hamedi%20and%20Elahe%20Mohammadi%2C%20who%20first%20reported%20on%20Jina%20Mahsa%E2%80%99s%20death%20in%20custody%E2%80%9D%2C%20said%20Viviana%20Krsticevic%2C%20Member%20of%20the%20FFM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%20received%20by%20the%20Fact-Finding%20Mission%2C%20at%20least%2026%20individuals%20have%20been%20sentenced%20to%20death%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20protests%20since%20November%202022%2C%20while%20dozens%20more%20have%20been%20charged%20with%20or%20face%20offences%20carrying%20the%20death%20penalty.%20At%20least%20seven%20men%20have%20been%20executed%20following%20hasty%20proceedings%2C%20amid%20serious%20allegations%20of%20rights%20violations%2C%20including%20of%20confessions%20extracted%20under%20torture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsh%20punishments%20continue%20to%20be%20meted%20out%20to%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20protests%2C%20including%20for%20exercising%20rights%20protected%20under%20international%20human%20rights%20law.%20They%20are%20being%20imposed%20following%20legal%20proceedings%20that%20lack%20transparency%20and%20fail%20to%20meet%20basic%20fair%20trial%20and%20due%20process%20guarantees%20under%20international%20human%20rights%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20particularly%20concerned%20about%20the%20many%20reports%20of%20harassment%20of%20family%20members%20seeking%20justice%20for%20their%20loved%20ones%2C%20including%20children%2C%20who%20were%20killed%20during%20the%20protests%E2%80%9D%2C%20Hossain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20months%20after%20the%20protests%20began%2C%20a%20series%20of%20alleged%20poisonings%20in%20dozens%20of%20schools%20across%2028%20provinces%20were%20reported.%20The%20FFM%20is%20investigating%20whether%20these%20alleged%20poisonings%20have%20been%20orchestrated%20as%20a%20means%20to%20punish%20or%20deter%20girls%20for%20their%20involvement%20in%20the%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20draft%20bills%20have%20been%20introduced%20since%20the%20protests%20and%20now%20await%20consideration%2C%20including%20before%20the%20Majles%2C%20or%20Iranian%20Parliament.%20If%20passed%2C%20they%20would%20impose%20harsher%20punishments%20on%20women%20and%20girls%20found%20in%20breach%20of%20forced%20veiling%20provisions%20and%20expose%20them%20to%20increased%20risks%20of%20violence%2C%20harassment%20and%20arbitrary%20detention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20and%20girl%20students%20have%20been%20reportedly%20suspended%20from%20their%20studies%20or%20banned%20from%20dormitories%20for%20their%20defiance%20of%20the%20compulsory%20veiling%20law%2C%20while%20businesses%20have%20been%20fined%20or%20closed%20for%20non-enforcement.%20The%20Fact-Finding%20Mission%20is%20concerned%20about%20the%20reported%20use%20of%20facial%20recognition%20technologies%20to%20identify%20and%20arrest%20women%20and%20girls%20failing%20to%20comply%20with%20forced%20veiling%20and%20to%20identify%20protestors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Fact-Finding%20Mission%20has%20sent%20seven%20letters%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20Iran%2C%20including%20repeated%20requests%20for%20a%20visit%20to%20Iran%20to%20gather%20information%20critical%20to%20its%20investigations.%20These%20have%20so%20far%20gone%20unanswered.%20The%20FFM%20has%20just%20yesterday%20met%20with%20the%20Iranian%20President%E2%80%99s%20of%20the%20recently%20appointed%20%E2%80%9CSpecial%20Committee%20to%20investigate%20the%202022%20unrests%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIran%20has%20an%20obligation%20to%20protect%20the%20rights%20of%20all%20people%20in%20the%20country%20and%20to%20hold%20accountable%20the%20individuals%20who%20are%20responsible%20for%20alleged%20rights%20violations%20related%20to%20the%20protests%20and%20address%20the%20root%20causes%20of%20these%20violations%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shaheen%20Sardar%20Ali%2C%20Member%20of%20the%20FFM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20of%20Iran%2C%20including%20women%20and%20girls%2C%20have%20fundamental%20rights%20to%20equality%2C%20truth%2C%20justice%2C%20accountability%20and%20reparations%20that%20must%20be%20upheld.%20We%20call%20on%20the%20Government%20of%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Iran%20to%20fully%20cooperate%20with%20our%20mandate%20and%20to%20ensure%20that%20all%20those%20affected%20have%20unhindered%20and%20safe%20access%20to%20providing%20evidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hossain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Fact-Finding%20Mission%20will%20present%20a%20comprehensive%20report%20on%20its%20findings%20to%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20during%20an%20interactive%20dialogue%20at%20its%2055th%20session%20in%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBackground%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20UN%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20mandated%20the%20Independent%20International%20Fact-Finding%20Mission%20on%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Iran%20on%2024%20November%202022%20to%20investigate%20alleged%20human%20rights%20violations%20in%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Iran%20related%20to%20the%20protests%20that%20began%20there%20on%2016%20September%202022%2C%20especially%20with%20respect%20to%20women%20and%20children.%20On%2020%20December%202022%2C%20the%20President%20of%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Council%20announced%20the%20appointment%20of%20Sara%20Hossain%20(Bangladesh)%2C%20Shaheen%20Sardar%20Ali%20(Pakistan)%20and%20Viviana%20Krsticevic%20(Argentina)%20to%20serve%20as%20the%20three%20independent%20members%20of%20the%20Mission%20and%20appointed%20Ms.%20Sara%20Hossain%20as%20its%20Chair.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689408398000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15120706%2FUntitled-design-4.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Firan-must-cease-crackdown-on-protesters-human-rights-situation-at-risk-says-fact-finding-mission%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Fact-Finding%20Mission%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20wave%20of%20executions%2C%20mass%20arrests%2C%20and%20detentions%2C%20following%20the%20death%20of%20Jina%20Mahsa%20Amini%20in%20custody%20last%20September.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Firan-must-cease-crackdown-on-protesters-human-rights-situation-at-risk-says-fact-finding-mission%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20the%20Resistance%20of%20Palestinians%20Has%20Been%20Defying%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Ongoing%20%E2%80%98Nakba%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F27083345%2F24545212292_5d8738816b_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%2C%20perhaps%2C%20crucial%20to%20define%20two%20terminologies%20at%20the%20very%20outset%20that%20defines%20the%20ongoing%20struggle%20for%20justice%20in%20Palestine-Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Sumud%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20which%20implies%20%E2%80%98steadfast%20perseverance%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20is%20a%20Palestinian%20cultural%20value%2C%20ideological%20theme%20and%20political%20strategy%20that%20first%20emerged%20among%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20through%20the%20experience%20of%20oppression%20and%20resistance%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%201967%20Six-Day%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20discrepancy%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Nakba%E2%80%99%20(Arabic%20for%20%E2%80%98catastrophe%E2%80%99)%20which%20%E2%80%98Sumud%E2%80%99%20seeks%20to%20confront%20through%20multiple%20forms%20of%20resistance%2C%20represents%20the%20Jewish%20intent%20of%20the%20permanent%20displacement%20of%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20Arabs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERecapping%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20%E2%80%98Nakba%E2%80%99%20of%20May%2015%2C%201948%2C%20750%2C000%20Palestinians%2C%20two-thirds%20of%20Palestine%E2%80%99s%20Arab%20population%2C%20were%20forced%20to%20flee%20their%20homes%20to%20accommodate%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20creation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeventy-five%20years%20later%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Palestinian%20refugees%20is%20over%20eight%20million.%20These%20agonising%20figures%20make%20Palestinians%20the%20largest%20and%20oldest%20unsettled%20refugee%20population%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20direct%20repression%20of%20Palestine%20began%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98Nakba%E2%80%99.%20Often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thecitizen.in%2Fworld%2Fisraels-ongoing-nakba-933142%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAlthough%2520regarded%2520by%2520many%2520as%2Cand%2520worse%252C%2520even%2520by%2520Palestinian%5C%22%3Ereferred%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Coriginal%20sin%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Israeli-Palestinian%20conflict%2C%20the%20refugee%20crisis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20core%20status%20questions%20that%20define%20the%20unsettled%20Israeli-Palestinian%20peace%20process.%20The%20remaining%20issues%20include%20the%20status%20of%20Jerusalem%2C%20Israeli%20settlements%2C%20borders%2C%20security%20and%20water%20rights%2C%20and%20Palestinian%20freedom%20of%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2029%2C%201947%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%20adopted%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Ftopic%2FUnited-Nations-Resolution-181%5C%22%3EPartition%20Resolution%20181%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20divide%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20former%20Palestinian%20mandate%20into%20Jewish%20and%20Arab%20states%20in%20May%201948.%20It%20was%20patently%20discriminatory.%20Palestinian-Arab%20leadership%20rejected%20the%20partition%20measures%20as%20unacceptable%2C%20given%20the%20inequality%20in%20the%20proposed%20population%20exchange%20and%20the%20transfer%20of%20one-third%20of%20Palestine%2C%20including%20its%20best%20agricultural%20land%2C%20to%20new%20Jewish%20arrivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20partitioned%20Palestine%20into%20Arab%20and%20Jewish%20states%2C%20with%20Jerusalem%20internationalised.%20Israel%20proclaimed%20its%20independence%20and%20in%20the%201948%20war%20that%20involved%20neighbouring%20Arab%20states%2C%20it%20expanded%20its%20territory%20of%20mandate%20Palestine%20to%2077%25%2C%20including%20the%20larger%20part%20of%20Jerusalem.%20Over%20half%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20Arab%20population%20fled%20or%20were%20expelled.%20Jordan%20and%20Egypt%20controlled%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20territory%20assigned%20by%20a%20UN%20resolution%20to%20the%20Arab%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FSix-Day_War%5C%22%3ESix-Day%20War%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20June%201967%20was%20fought%20between%20Israel%20and%20the%20Arab%20countries%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FEgypt%5C%22%3EEgypt%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FJordan%5C%22%3EJordan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FSyria%5C%22%3ESyria%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20war%20was%20decisively%20calamitous%20for%20Palestine%20and%20its%20neighbours.%20Following%20the%20war%2C%20the%20territory%20held%20by%20Israel%20expanded%20significantly%20and%20Israel%20captured%20more%20territory%20that%20is%20still%20deemed%20occupied.%20Israel%20still%20does%20not%20show%20any%20intent%20to%20return%20the%20land%20occupied%20under%20hostilities.%20The%20war%20brought%20about%20a%20second%20exodus%20of%20Palestinians%2C%20estimated%20to%20be%20at%20half%20a%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Security%20Council%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Funispal%2Fdocument%2Fauto-insert-184858%2F%5C%22%3EResolution%20%3C%2Fa%3Eformulated%20the%20principles%20of%20a%20just%20and%20lasting%20peace%2C%20including%20an%20Israeli%20withdrawal%20from%20territories%20occupied%20in%20the%20conflict%2C%20an%20appropriate%20settlement%20of%20the%20refugee%20problem%2C%20and%20the%20termination%20of%20all%20claims%2C%20and%20of%20hostilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201973%20Arab-Israeli%20War%2C%20called%20the%20Yom%20Kippur%20War%2FRamadan%20War%2C%20the%20Fourth%20Arab-Israeli%20War%2C%20was%20an%20armed%20conflict%20fought%20from%20October%206%20to%2025%2C%201973%20between%20Israel%20and%20a%20coalition%20of%20Arab%20states%20led%20by%20Egypt%20and%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Funispal%2Fdata-collection%2Fsecurity-council%2F%5C%22%3ESecurity%20Council%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20for%20peace%20negotiations%20between%20the%20parties%20concerned.%20In%20the%20next%20year%2C%20the%20General%20Assembly%20reaffirmed%20the%20inalienable%20rights%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20to%20self-determination%2C%20national%20independence%2C%20sovereignty%2C%20and%20to%20return%20to%20their%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20established%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Funispal%2Fcommittee%2F%5C%22%3ECommittee%20on%20the%20Exercise%20of%20the%20Inalienable%20Rights%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20People%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20conferred%20on%20the%20Palestine%20Liberation%20Organisation%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Funispal%2Fdocument%2Fauto-insert-180059%2F%5C%22%3Estatus%20of%20observer%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20Assembly%20and%20in%20the%20UN%20conferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Israel%20persists%20in%20ceaselessly%20grabbing%20Palestinian%20land.%20It%20has%20fought%20and%20won%20eight%20recognised%20wars%20with%20its%20neighbouring%20Arab%20states%2C%20including%20two%20major%20Palestinian%20Arab%20uprisings%20known%20as%20the%20First%20Intifada%20and%20the%20Second%20Intifada%2C%20(Intifada%20in%20Arabic%20means%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98rebellion%E2%80%99)%20and%20a%20series%20of%20armed%20engagements%20in%20Palestinian%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F1948_Arab%25E2%2580%2593Israeli_War%5C%22%3E1948%20Arab-Israeli%20War%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FPalestinian_fedayeen%5C%22%3EPalestinian%20%3Cem%3EFedayeen%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(%3Cem%3EFedayeen%3C%2Fem%3E%20means%20someone%20who%20redeems%20himself%20by%20risking%20or%20sacrificing%20his%20life)%2C%20when%20Palestinian%20militants%20engaged%20in%20insurgency%20(1950s-1960s)%20to%20which%20there%20was%20furious%20retaliation%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FIsrael_Defense_Forces%5C%22%3EIsrael%20Defence%20Forces%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20uprisings%20included%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFirst_Intifada%5C%22%3EFirst%20%3Cem%3EIntifada%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Arabic%20for%20%E2%80%9Cuprising%E2%80%9D)%2C%20the%20first%20large-scale%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FPalestinian_people%5C%22%3EPalestinian%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FUprising%5C%22%3Euprising%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0against%20Israel%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FWest_Bank%5C%22%3EWest%20Bank%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FGaza_Strip%5C%22%3EGaza%20Strip%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%201987-1990.%20This%20%3Cem%3EIntifada%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20a%20robust%20display%20of%20the%20militancy%20and%20muscle%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20youth.%20It%20led%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fremix.aljazeera.com%2Faje%2FPalestineRemix%2Fthe-price-of-oslo.html%23%2F14%5C%22%3EOslo%20Accords%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20held%20out%20a%20mirage%20of%20peace.%20The%20Oslo%20Accords%20lacked%20political%20construct%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20collapsed.%20Its%20failure%20led%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FSecond_Intifada%5C%22%3ESecond%20%3Cem%3EIntifada%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(2000-2005)%2C%20a%20period%20of%20intensified%20violence%2C%20which%20began%20in%20late%20September%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20multiple%20vigorous%20clashes%20occurred%20such%20as%20the%20three-week%20armed%20conflict%20between%20Israel%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FHamas%5C%22%3EHamas%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20winter%20of%202008-2009.%20Israeli%20forces%20attacked%20military%20and%20civilian%20targets%2C%20police%20stations%2C%20and%20government%20buildings.%20The%20uninterrupted%20airstrikes%2C%20artillery%20shelling%20and%20ground%20operations%20resulted%20in%20the%20killing%20of%201%2C383%20Palestinians%2C%20including%20333%20children%20and%20114%20women%2C%20and%20injured%20over%205%2C300%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20appetite%20for%20killings%20seemed%20unquenchable.%20By%20November%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2012_Israeli_operation_in_the_Gaza_Strip%5C%22%3E2012%2C%20it%20launched%20an%20operation%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20it%20launched%20yet%20another%20war%20in%20Gaza%20in%20response%20to%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20American-sponsored%20peace%20talks%2C%20and%20attempts%20by%20rival%20Palestinian%20factions%20to%20form%20a%20coalition%20government.%20This%20led%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20rocket%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FHamas%5C%22%3EHamas%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0militants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%20that%20year%2C%20there%20were%20riots%20between%20Jews%20and%20Arabs%20in%20Israeli%20cities.%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%20sent%20military%20rockets%20into%20Israel%2C%20and%20Israel%20viciously%20retaliated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20first%20five%20months%20of%202023%2C%20the%20number%20of%20people%20killed%20by%20the%20Israeli%20forces%20have%20tripled%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20figures%20in%20January%20and%20December%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmjad%20Mitri%2C%20a%20human%20rights%20lawyer%2C%20points%20out%3A%20%E2%80%9CMillions%20of%20Palestinians%20worldwide%20live%20in%20forced%20diaspora%20and%20are%20cut%20off%20from%20their%20homeland%20by%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20colonial%20practices%20and%20policies.%20The%20Zionist%20movement%20and%20the%20army%20has%20displaced%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20population%20and%20in%20turn%20created%20numerous%20laws%2C%20regulations%2C%20and%20military%20orders%20such%20as%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Infiltration%20Law%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20military%20orders%20to%20prevent%20Palestinians%20from%20returning%20to%20their%20homes%20and%20properties.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIsrael%20marks%20Palestinians%20who%20try%20to%20do%20so%20as%20%E2%80%9Cinfiltrators%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20has%20deported%20or%20even%20shot%20at%20them%20on%20sight.%20Israel%20has%20created%20a%20privileged%20colonial%20status%2C%20which%20in%20all%20facets%20of%20life%2C%20including%20the%20political%2C%20social%2C%20and%20cultural%20levels%2C%20is%20superior%20to%20that%20of%20non-Jewish%20Palestinians.%20Whether%20this%20system%20is%20labeled%20as%20apartheid%2C%20colonial%20rule%2C%20or%20Zionist%20state%20ideology%2C%20it%20is%20a%20manifestation%20of%20control%20and%20domination%20of%20one%20people%20over%20another%20that%20leaves%20no%20room%20for%20alternative%20interpretation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20mindset%20seeks%20to%20erase%20Palestinian%20identity%20and%20history%20and%20wipe%20Palestine%20off%20the%20map.%20Israel%20makes%20the%20fictitious%20claim%20that%20Palestinians%20and%20Palestine%20never%20existed%3B%20they%20were%20simply%20scattered%20groups%20of%20people%20living%20in%20the%20area%20before%201948.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDavid%20Ben-Gurion%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20first%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20believes%20that%20the%20new%20generation%20of%20the%20dispossessed%20and%20displaced%20indigenous%20population%20will%20self-erase%20their%20heritage%20and%20sense%20of%20belonging%20to%20their%20land.%20Israel%20must%20obstruct%20them%20from%20making%20their%20claim%20that%20they%20have%20the%20right%20to%20return