p%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20only%20thought%20that%20Adam%20was%20sad%20for%20his%20friend%2C%20but%20never%20thought%20at%20the%20beginning%20that%20he%20was%20entertaining%20the%20idea%20of%20death%20himself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20witnessed%20an%20occupation%20raid%20for%20the%20first%20time%20when%20he%20was%20five%2C%20and%20grew%20up%20seeing%20people%20in%20the%20camp%20and%20neighbourhood%20being%20arrested%20or%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountless%20families%20welcome%20mourners%20into%20their%20house.%20The%20open-house%20ritual%20usually%20lasts%20for%20three%20days%2C%20but%20it%20had%20been%20a%20week%20since%2014-year-old%20Amer%20Khmour%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmondoweiss.net%2F2023%2F01%2Fpalestinians-killed-by-israel-share-their-last-will-and-testament%2F%5C%22%3Ewas%20killed%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Israeli%20soldiers%20during%20their%20last%20raid%20into%20Dheisheh%2C%20and%20mourners%20kept%20pouring%20into%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhmour%20didn%E2%80%99t%20talk%20a%20lot%20about%20politics%2C%20or%20about%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20camp%2C%20as%20he%20was%20mostly%20having%20fun%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20like%20all%20boys%20his%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnarendra-modi-india-palestine%5C%22%3EDoes%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20India%20Care%20About%20Palestine%20Any%20More%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColonialism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20stealth%20and%20occupying%20presence%20on%20Palestinian%20land%2C%20employing%20militaristic%20strategies%20rooted%20in%20colonial-racist%20ideologies%2C%20results%20in%20assaults%20targeting%20children%20and%20youngsters.%20It%20even%20targets%20the%20elderly%20who%20only%20ask%20for%20their%20right%20to%20liberation%20and%20dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Britain%20abandoned%20their%20mandate%20and%20handed%20it%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%20would%20choose%20sides%20and%20advocate%20for%20an%20uneven%20resolution%20in%20favour%20of%20Zionist%20demands%2C%20rather%20than%20addressing%20the%20concerns%20of%20Palestine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZionism%20is%20an%20ideology%20which%20shoves%20Palestinians%20to%20the%20margins%20of%20political%20space.%20It%20is%20aligned%20with%20the%20movement%20to%20establish%20a%20Jewish%20homeland%20in%20Palestine%20during%20the%2019th%20and%2020th%20centuries.%20Its%20history%20and%20significance%20are%20a%20matter%20of%20contention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Ffeatures%2F2018%2F11%2F2%2Fmore-than-a-century-on-the-balfour-declaration-explained%5C%22%3EBalfour%20Declaration%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20the%20direct%20outcome%20of%20a%20sustained%20effort%20by%20the%20Zionist%20Organisation%20to%20establish%20a%20Jewish%20state%20in%20Palestine.%20It%20meant%20that%20Palestinians%20faced%20the%20prospect%20of%20being%20outnumbered%20by%20unlimited%20immigration%2C%20and%20of%20losing%20control%20of%20Palestine%20to%20the%20Zionist%20drive%20for%20sole%20sovereignty%20over%20a%20country%20that%20was%20then%20almost%20completely%20Arabic%20in%20population%20and%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20achieve%20justice%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20imperative%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20the%20misrule%20of%20Occupied%20Palestinian%20territories%2C%20which%20are%20subjected%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20racist%20laws%2C%20colonial%20practices%2C%20and%20an%20apartheid%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two-state%20solution%2C%20as%20a%20means%20to%20end%20the%20Palestine-Israel%20conflict%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20no%20longer%20viable.%20By%20clinging%20to%20this%20impossible%20solution%2C%20the%20international%20community%20prolongs%20Palestinian%20agony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F3%2F3%2Fisraeli-settler-attacks-against-palestinians-by-the-numbers%5C%22%3E750%2C000%20illegal%20settlers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20East%20Jerusalem%20the%20principle%20of%20separation%20of%20the%20two%20communities%20is%20an%20absolute%20non-starter.%20Achieving%20lasting%20peace%20in%20Palestine-Israel%20requires%20an%20innovative%20solution%2C%20which%20must%20prioritise%20justice%20above%20all%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERanjan%20Solomon%20is%20a%20political%20commentator%2C%20writer%2C%20and%20human%20rights%20activist.%20His%20work%20for%20solidarity%20with%20Palestinians%20began%20in%201989%20and%20continues%20to%20this%20day%20through%20global%20and%20national%20networks.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689407087000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F27083345%2F24545212292_5d8738816b_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhow-the-resistance-of-palestinians-has-been-defying-israels-ongoing-nakba%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20military%20power%20of%20Israel%20has%20failed%20to%20curb%20Palestinian%20resistance.%20Palestinians%20are%20convinced%20that%20the%20might%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20colonialist-apartheid%20structure%20will%2C%20one%20day%2C%20crumble%2C%20due%20to%20its%20lack%20of%20moral%20legitimacy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhow-the-resistance-of-palestinians-has-been-defying-israels-ongoing-nakba%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tajdar%3A%20Kriti%20should%20avoid%20the%20role%20of%20Meena%20Kumari%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689406494000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101775516%2Cimgsize-2371219.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftajdar-amrohi-kriti-sanon-is-a-good-actress-but