%20starring%20in%20the%20upcoming%20%3Cem%3EStar%20Wars%3A%20Ahsoka%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Allison%20Janney%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20West%20Wing%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0fame%2C%20were%20among%20the%20more%20famous%20members%20of%20SAG-AFTRA%2C%20the%20actors%E2%80%99%20union%2C%20to%20demonstrate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20striking%20actors%20joined%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhollywood-actors-join-writers-in-strike%2Fa-66206517%5C%22%3Ethousands%20of%20members%20of%20the%20Writers%20Guild%20of%20America%20(WGA)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20walked%20off%20sets%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20Hollywood%20saw%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdouble%20strike%E2%80%9D%20of%20actors%20and%20writers%20was%20in%201960.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EActors%20union%20snaps%20back%20at%20AI%20proposal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStriking%20actors%C2%A0are%20demanding%C2%A0stronger%20safeguards%20on%20the%20use%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Ft-42133476%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20assurances%20that%20digital%20images%20will%20not%20be%20used%20without%20their%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAMPTP%2C%C2%A0which%20represents%20employers%20including%20Disney%2C%20Netflix%2C%20Amazon%20and%20others%2C%20said%20it%20had%20agreed%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgroundbreaking%20AI%20proposal%E2%80%9D%20to%20mitigate%C2%A0these%20concerns%20by%20protecting%20performers%E2%80%99%20digital%20likeness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESAG-AFTRA%20chief%20negotiator%20Duncan%20Crabtree-Ireland%20sad%20that%20studios%20had%20proposed%20that%20background%20actors%20be%20offered%20a%20days%20pay%20to%20have%20their%20likeness%20scanned%2C%20which%20entertainment%20firms%20could%20permanently%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20if%20you%20think%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20groundbreaking%20proposal%2C%20I%20suggest%20you%20think%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAMPTP%20said%20that%20the%20union%E2%80%99s%20claim%20was%20false%20and%20that%20the%20proposal%20would%20only%20cover%20the%20motion%20picture%20a%20given%20background%20performer%20is%20employed%20for%2C%20with%20future%20use%20of%20replicas%20being%20subject%20to%20negotiation%20and%20a%20minimum%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStudios%20and%20actors%20wrangle%20over%20pay%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESAG-AFTRA%20is%20asking%20studios%20for%20pay%20rises%20in%20line%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Finflation%2Ft-19070269%5C%22%3Einflation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisney%20CEO%20Bob%20Iger%20dismissed%20this%20demand%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunrealistic%E2%80%9D%20earlier%20this%20week.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cshame%E2%80%9D%20that%20strikes%20would%20damage%20the%20entertainment%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20that%20when%20Bob%20Iger%20talks%20about%20what%20a%20shame%20it%20is%2C%20he%20needs%20to%20remember%20that%20in%201980%2C%20CEOs%20like%20him%20made%2030%20times%20what%20their%20lowest%20worker%20was%20making%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sean%20Gunn%2C%20who%20acted%20in%20the%20film%20%3Cem%3EGuardians%20of%20the%20Galaxy%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20Iger%20now%20%E2%80%9Cmakes%20400%20times%20what%20his%20lowest%20worker%20is.%20And%20I%20think%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20shame%2C%20Bob.%20And%20maybe%20you%20should%20take%20a%20look%20in%20the%20mirror%20and%20ask%20yourself%2C%20%E2%80%98Why%20is%20that%3F'%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20union%20is%20also%20demanding%20that%20streaming%20services%20disclose%20viewership%20figures%20so%20that%20actors%20can%20receive%20residuals%20every%20time%20a%20production%20is%20aired.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHollywood%20strike%20reaches%20Germany%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActors%20Ryan%20Gosling%20and%20Margot%20Robbie%20will%20not%20attend%20the%20Berlin%20premiere%20of%20their%20film%20%3Cem%3EBarbie%