en%20killed%20and%20three%20were%20missing%20as%20heavy%20rains%20flooded%20South%20Korea%2C%20officials%20said%20Saturday%2C%20with%20thousands%20told%20to%20evacuate%20their%20homes%20due%20to%20an%20overflowing%20dam.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fheavy-rains-flooding-leave-seven-dead-in-south-korea%2Farticleshow%2F101775266.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fheavy-rains-flooding-leave-seven-dead-in-south-korea%2Famp_articleshow%2F101775266.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fheavy-rains-flooding-leave-seven-dead-in-south-korea%2Famp_articleshow%2F101775266.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jalgaon%3A%20Based%20on%20Right-Wing%20Activist's%20Complaint%2C%20Collector%20Bans%20Namaz%20at%20800-Year-Old%20Mosque%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15110417%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-15-at-10.41.29-AM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20as%20long%20as%20Aslam%20recalls%2C%20men%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%20have%20been%20congregating%20inside%20the%20Jumma%20Masjid%20in%20Jalgaon%E2%80%99s%20Erandol%20Taluka%20five%20times%20a%20day%20to%20offer%20namaz.%20The%20800-year-old%20structure%20is%20an%20important%20place%20of%20worship%20in%20northern%20Maharashtra%20and%20a%20property%20registered%20under%20the%20Waqf%20Board.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20it%20has%20suddenly%20become%20inaccessible%20to%20the%20community%20after%20the%20district%20collector%20passed%20an%20interim%20restraining%20order%20while%20hearing%20a%20complaint%20filed%20by%20a%20right-wing%20organisation.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20collector%20issued%20an%20order%20under%20section%20144%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%2C%20immediately%20banning%20prayers%20on%20the%20premises.%20In%20the%20order%2C%20the%20collector%20also%20directed%20police%20deployment%20in%20the%20area.%20The%20collector%20asked%20the%20tahsildar%20to%20take%20charge%20of%20the%20mosque%2C%20which%20he%20described%20as%20%E2%80%9Cdisputed%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20collector%E2%80%99s%20interim%20restraining%20order%20and%20his%20power%20to%20pass%20it%20have%20been%20challenged%20before%20the%20Aurangabad%20bench%20of%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAslam%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Jumma%20Masjid%20Trust%2C%20fears%20that%20the%20unprecedented%20order%20marks%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20communalisation%20of%20a%20centuries-old%20mosque%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20complaint%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20centuries-old%20mosque%20suddenly%20became%20a%20site%20of%20controversy%20because%20of%20a%20complaint%20filed%20by%20an%20unregistered%20organisation%20called%20%E2%80%9CPandavwada%20Sangharsh%20Samiti%E2%80%9D.%20The%20complainant%2C%20Prasad%20Madhusudan%20Dandawate%2C%20moved%20a%20petition%20before%20the%20Jalgaon%20district%20collector%20Aman%20Mittal%20in%20mid-May.%20Dandawate%2C%20according%20to%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fprasad.dandawate%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFacebook%20profile%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%20and%20Bajrang%20Dal.%20In%20his%20complaint%2C%20Dandawate%20claimed%20that%20the%20mosque%20was%20built%20over%20a%20Hindu%20place%20of%20worship%20and%20is%20illegal%20and%20should%20be%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20state%20authorities.%20The%20complainant%20also%20claims%20that%20the%20Jumma%20Masjid%20Trust%20has%20%E2%80%9Cillegally%E2%80%9D%20encroached%20over%20the%20space.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Jumma%20Masjid%20Trust%20members%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20they%20were%20unaware%20of%20the%20claims%20made%20until%20they%20received%20a%20notice%20end%20of%20June.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20then%2C%20the%20collector%20had%20already%20been%20conducting%20hearings.%20In%20a%20restricted%20time%2C%20we%20were%20asked%20to%20defend%20our%20case.%20And%20on%20July%2011%2C%20the%20collector%20simply%20passed%20a%20restraining%20order%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aslam%2C%20one%20of%20the%20ad-hoc%20members%20of%20the%20trust%20committee%2C%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlong%20with%20the%20mosque%E2%80%99s%20trust%20committee%2C%20the%20Waqf%20Board%20and%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20(ASI)%20too%20were%20issued%20notice%20by%20the%20collector.%20The%20ASI%20has%20supported%20the%20trust%E2%80%99s%20claims%20that%20it%20is%20an%20ancient%20structure.%20It%20said%20that%20since%20the%20time%20the%20ASI%20was%20involved%20in%201986%2C%20prayers%20have%20been%20offered%20inside%20the%20mosque%20premises.%20The%20ASI%20stated%20that%20the%20mosque%20has%20been%20an%20open%20and%20accessible%20space%20for%20the%20Muslim%20community%20for%20time%20immemorial.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Waqf%20Board%2C%20citing%20the%20Waqf%20law%2C%20challenged%20the%20collector%E2%80%99s%20power%20to%20preside%20over%20the%20hearing%20of%20the%20complaint.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20its%20response%2C%20signed%20by%20Junaid%20Sayyad%2C%20the%20deputy%20chief%20executive%20officer%20(CEO)%20of%20the%20Waqf%20Board%2C%20the%20board%20points%20to%20the%20relevant%20sections%20of%20the%20law%20that%20bars%20any%20department%20other%20than%20the%20Waqf%20from%20looking%20at%20disputes%20arising%20out%20of%20titles%20and%20related%20property%20issues%20of%20those%20registered%20under%20the%20board.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15110405%2FScreenshot-2023-07-15-at-11.02.47-AM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15110405%2FScreenshot-2023-07-15-at-11.02.47-AM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15110405%2FScreenshot-2023-07-15-at-11.02.47-AM-300x126.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15110405%2FScreenshot-2023-07-15-at-11.02.47-AM-1024x430.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663288%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFile%20image%20of%20Muslim%20men%20offering%20prayers%20at%20the%20Jumma%20Masjid%20in%20Jalgaon%E2%80%99s%20Erandol.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Outside%20collector%E2%80%99s%20mandate%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoin%20Tahsildar%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20board%2C%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20collector%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20issue%20a%20restraining%20order%20was%20clearly%20outside%20his%20mandate%20and%20it%20infringed%20on%20the%20legal%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20Waqf%20tribunal.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20collector%20can%20interfere%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20handling%20the%20law-and-order%20aspects%20here%3B%20everything%20else%20is%20the%20Waqf%20board%E2%80%99s%20responsibility.%20The%20property%20has%20been%20registered%20with%20the%20board%20since%202009%20and%20there%20is%20no%20ambiguity%20in%20that%20aspect%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tahsildar%20clarified.%20He%20further%20added%20that%20the%20board%2C%20in%20its%20response%20to%20the%20collector%2C%20had%20clearly%20spelt%20out%20the%20legal%20position.%20%E2%80%9CYet%2C%20it%20was%20overlooked%20while%20issuing%20the%20restraining%20order%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tahsildar%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20challenged%20the%20interim%20order%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tahsildar%20added.%20The%20hearing%20in%20the%20matter%20was%20scheduled%20for%20July%2013%20but%20later%20the%20collector%20deferred%20the%20hearing%20to%20July%2018.%20The%20interim%20restraining%20order%20will%20continue%20until%20the%20next%20hearing%20date.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Masjid%20Trust%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20moved%20the%20high%20court%20with%20documents%20that%20are%20from%20pre-independence%20times%20%E2%80%93%20including%20court%20orders%20from%20time%20to%20time%20and%20those%20passed%20by%20the%20British%20Indian%20government.%20After%20the%201960s%20too%2C%20there%20has%20been%20periodic%20updation%20of%20documents%20and%20the%20mosque%20has%20been%20earmarked%20as%20an%20ancient%20monument%2C%20the%20petition%20mentions.%20The%20petitioners%20have%20also%20complained%20about%20the%20collector%E2%80%99s%20unwillingness%20to%20give%20them%20a%20fair%20hearing.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20learned%20Collector%20was%20not%20in%20a%20mood%20to%20hear%20anything%20from%20the%20petitioner%20and%20without%20giving%20any%20opportunity%20to%20the%20petitioner%20on%2011.07.2023%20the%20learned%20Collector%2C%20Jalgaon%2C%20passed%20an%20order%20under%20Section%20144%20and%20145%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20petition%20alleges.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689399920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjalgaon-right-wing-activist-complaint-juma-masjid-namaz-ban%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Jumma%20Masjid%20in%20Jalgaon%E2%80%99s%20Erandol%20is%20a%20property%20registered%20under%20the%20Waqf%20Board.%20Even%20though%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20supported%20the%20mosque%20trust%E2%80%99s%20claims%2C%20the%20collector%20has%20passed%20an%20unprecedented%20interim%20restraining%20order.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vicky-Katrina%20jet%20off%20to%20celebrate%20latter's%20bday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689398901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101774578%2Cimgsize-59410.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvicky-kaushal-and-katrina-kaif-take-off-to-an-undisclosed-location-before-the-actresss-40th-birthday%2Farticleshow%2F101774565.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F101774565.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKatrina%20Kaif%20and%20Vicky%20Kaushal%20who%20has%20recently%20returned%20from%20US%20trip%2C%20take%20off%20for%20another%20holiday%20to%20celebrate%20the%20actress's%2040th%20birthday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvicky-kaushal-and-katrina-kaif-take-off-to-an-undisclosed-location-before-the-actresss-40th-birthday%2Farticleshow%2F101774565.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karnataka%20Budget%20Sticks%20Price%20Tags%20on%20Poll%20Guarantees%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15101344%2FF0WBGl3XwAAyms0.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20India%20Cable%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%C2%A0a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%C2%A0The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3Eclick%20here%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20manufacturer%20of%20a%20brand%20gives%20a%20guarantee%20to%20a%20consumer%2C%20she%20usually%20regards%20it%20with%20suspicion.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20to%20be%20a%20hitch%20somewhere%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20thinks.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20announced%20five%20poll%20guarantees%20just%20two%20months%20ago%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20possible%20that%20the%20voter%20in%20Karnataka%20trusted%20that%20these%20would%20not%20come%20at%20a%20price%2C%20and%20hence%20gave%20a%20resounding%20victory%20to%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20after%20Siddaramaiah%E2%80%99s%20first%20budget%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20these%20guarantees%20may%20have%20come%20at%20a%20price%20%E2%80%95%20the%20price%20of%20slower%20growth%20and%20employment%2C%20sub-optimal%20education%20and%20healthcare%2C%20and%20the%20risk%20of%20depleting%20the%20treasury.%20While%20this%20impact%20would%20not%20have%20sunk%20in%20yet%2C%20it%20should%20be%20a%20concern%20for%20all%20citizens%20who%20want%20Karnataka%20and%20its%20people%20to%20progress%20and%20find%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20a%20budget%20spend%20of%20Rs%20327%2C000%20crore%2C%20the%20five%20guarantees%20are%20going%20to%20cost%20the%20government%20Rs%2052%2C000%20crore%20(on%20an%20annualised%20basis)%2C%20or%20about%2016%25%20of%20the%20total.%20To%20accommodate%20this%2C%20the%20CM%20has%20reduced%20spending%20in%20several%20key%20areas%20with%20very%20significant%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%20of%20all%2C%20capital%20expenditure%20(capex)%2C%20which%20is%20meant%20to%20stimulate%20growth%2C%20is%20being%20reduced%20from%20Rs%2052%2C700%20crore%20to%20Rs%2051%2C000%20crore%2C%20or%203%25.%20Taking%20inflation%20into%20account%2C%20the%20real%20reduction%20could%20be%20up%20to%2010%25.%20Within%20this%2C%20capex%20on%20irrigation%20projects%20is%20down%20a%20massive%2021%25.%20Industry%20and%20transport%20have%20also%20been%20reduced.%20Capex%20is%20meant%20to%20build%20productive%20assets%2C%20to%20stimulate%20income%20and%20employment%20growth.%20Hence%2C%20this%20reduction%20will%20impact%20the%20growth%20of%20our%20state%20as%20well%20as%20future%20employment%2C%20unless%20it%20is%20overcompensated%20by%20private%20sector%20investment%20or%20efficiency%20in%20governance.%20However%2C%20key%20sectors%20like%20irrigation%20are%20unlikely%20to%20be%20compensated%20by%20private%20sector%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20large-scale%20budget%20reductions%20of%2020-30%25%20in%20agriculture%20and%20rural%20development%20will%20impact%20growth%20and%20employment.%20The%20stimulus%20that%20the%20agri-rural%20sector%20and%20other%20employment-generating%20sectors%20need%20is%20jeopardised%20by%20lower%20allocations%2C%20impacting%20peoples%E2%80%99%20earning%20capacities%20and%20increasing%20their%20dependence%20on%20public%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirdly%2C%20the%20outlay%20on%20education%20is%20coming%20down%20from%2011.4%25%20to%20about%2010%25.%20Considering%20the%20dire%20state%20of%20public%20education%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20school%20pass%20rates%20and%20learning%20levels%20are%20critically%20low%2C%20this%20is%20a%20serious%20concern.%20It%20means%20that%20poor%20and%20middle-class%20parents%20will%20have%20to%20continue%20spending%20a%20high%20share%20of%20their%20incomes%20on%20sending%20their%20children%20to%20private%20schools%20and%20colleges%20(often%20run%20by%20politicians%20for%20revenue!).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outlay%20on%20health%2C%20which%20was%20already%20very%20low%2C%20is%20down%20from%204.7%25%20to%204.5%25.%20Here%2C%20one%20option%20may%20be%20to%20improve%20efficiency%20by%20reducing%20rent-seeking%20by%20officialdom%20in%20the%20delivery%20of%20health%20services.%20Until%20then%2C%20the%20poor%20and%20middle-class%20will%20continue%20to%20have%20to%20continue%20to%20pay%20private%20clinics%20and%20hospitals%20for%20expensive%20diagnostic%20tests%20and%20treatment%2C%20instead%20of%20getting%20quality%2C%20free%20healthcare%20from%20the%20government.%20Reaching%20a%20basic%20level%20of%20health%20security%20through%20improved%20public%20health%20facilities%20will%20require%20significantly%20higher%20expenditure%20and%20more%20efficient%20use%20of%20current%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20this%20budget%20increases%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20depleted%20treasury.%20This%20is%20both%20due%20to%20aggressive%20assumptions%20and%20the%20increasing%20debt%20and%20interest%20repayment%20burden.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20budget%20assumes%20a%20massive%2018%25%20increase%20in%20GST%20collections.%20It%20assumes%20a%20marginal%203.7%25%20increase%20in%20pension%20payments%20and%20a%20significant%20decrease%20in%20expenditure%20for%20%E2%80%9Crelief%20from%20natural%20calamities%E2%80%9D.%20The%20state%20energy%20sector%20is%20already%20on%20oxygen%20and%20there%20is%20only%20lip%20service%20to%20address%20that%20issue.%20The%20spend%20on%20servicing%20debt%20will%20increase%20by%2023%25%20over%20the%20previous%20year.%20Indeed%2C%20the%20spend%20on%20these%20two%20heads%20which%20was%20about%2013%25%20five%20years%20ago%20has%20now%20ballooned%20to%2018%25!%20At%20this%20rate%2C%20eventually%2C%20the%20state%20will%20either%20be%20forced%20to%20increase%20taxes%20or%20lower%20developmental%20spend%20to%20avoid%20a%20debt%20trap!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20more%20balanced%2C%20sustainable%20approach%20was%20required.%20For%20example%2C%20when%20AAP%20came%20to%20power%20in%20Delhi%2C%20it%20gave%20free%20electricity%20and%20bus%20rides%20for%20women.%20However%2C%20it%20also%20transformed%20school%20education%20and%20healthcare.%20And%20it%20did%20all%20this%20while%20consistently%20delivering%20a%20surplus%20revenue%20budget%20and%20ensuring%20that%20interest%20and%20debt%20payments%20were%20manageable.%20The%20secret%20is%20to%20control%20waste%20and%20corruption%20and%20use%20the%20resources%20thus%20freed%20up%20for%20good%20public%20work.%20Some%20may%20argue%20that%20Delhi%20is%20unique%20as%20it%20is%20a%20small%20state%20and%20has%20always%20had%20ample%20resources%2C%20but%20some%20of%20the%20principles%20it%20adopted%20for%20improving%20social%20infrastructure%20are%20worth%20examining.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20guarantees%20seem%20to%20be%20coming%20at%20a%20substantial%20price%2C%20as%20revealed%20in%20this%20budget.%20Siddaramaiah%20will%20need%20to%20go%20beyond%20budget%20accounting%20jugglery%20and%20find%20resources%20to%20fund%20these%20guarantees%20without%20compromising%20balanced%2C%20equitable%20growth%20and%20employment%2C%20or%20voters%20will%20feel%20justifiably%20duped.%20This%20is%20the%20real%20guarantee%20that%20this%20government%20must%20give%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Karnataka%20in%20the%20longer%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPrakash%20Nedungadi%20is%20a%20former%20president%20of%20Madura%20Garments%20and%20stood%20for%20the%20Karnataka%20assembly%20elections%20from%20Central%20Bengaluru%20on%20an%20AAP%20ticket.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689397207000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F15101344%2FF0WBGl3XwAAyms0.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fkarnataka-budget-price-tag-poll-guarantees%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20clear%20that%20these%20guarantees%20may%20have%20come%20at%20a%20price%20%E2%80%93%20the%20price%20of%20slower%20growth%20and%20employment%2C%20sub-optimal%20education%20and%20healthcare%2C%20and%20the%20risk%20of%20depleting%20the%20treasury.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8