023%2F07%2Fpackaging-1689256526.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpackaging-1689256526-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpackaging-1689256526-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpackaging-1689256526-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fpackaging-1689256526-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323769%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOld%20butter%20paper%20was%20used%20to%20wrap%20gifts.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20big%20aspect%20of%20Indian%20weddings%20is%20the%20gifts.%20While%20going%20through%20her%20attic%2C%20Anupama%20found%20a%20huge%20bundle%20of%20butter%20paper%20which%20she%20had%20stowed%20away%20after%20her%20son%E2%80%99s%20thread%20ceremony%20in%202004.%20She%20used%20that%20to%20pack%20the%20gifts%20for%20the%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20gave%20everyone%20naturally%20dyed%20blouse%20pieces.%20Even%20if%20one%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20stitch%20it%2C%20they%E2%80%99ll%20definitely%20hand%20it%20over%20to%20someone%20else.%20I%20also%20used%20all%20the%20%3Cem%3Earishina%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Ekumkuma%20(turmeric%20and%20vermillion%20powder)%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20I%20had%20at%20home%20and%20packed%20them%20in%20papers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anupama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20used%20only%20fresh%20flowers%20for%20decorations.%20Later%20on%2C%20the%20bride%E2%80%99s%20friends%20sent%20the%20flowers%20to%20a%20studio%20in%20Mumbai%20which%20used%20them%20as%20natural%20dyes%20and%20created%20clothes%20for%20the%20couple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuf6roDg0sV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloadi