inds%20Lucknow%E2%80%99s%20Nawabs%20to%20Kolkata%3A%20Packing%20My%20Family%E2%80%99s%20Royal%20Legacy%20in%20a%20Historic%20Biryani%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%201856%2C%20King%20Wajid%20Ali%20Shah%2C%20the%20last%20nawab%20of%20Lucknow%2C%20was%20exiled%20by%20the%20British%20to%20Metiabruz%2C%20a%20suburb%20of%20Calcutta%20(now%20Kolkata).%20Heartbroken%20to%20leave%20behind%20his%20dear%20city%2C%20the%20king%20established%20a%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Echota%20%3C%2Fem%3E(miniature)%20Lucknow%E2%80%99%20in%20Metiabruz%20to%20keep%20the%20sense%20of%20familiarity%20and%20the%20memories%20of%20his%20city%20alive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20move%20would%20go%20on%20to%20influence%20Calcutta%E2%80%99s%20local%20culture%20in%20numerous%20ways.%20For%20one%2C%20Wajid%20Ali%20introduced%20sports%20like%20kite-flying%20and%20cock-fighting%2C%20as%20well%20as%20poetry%20in%20the%20region.%20Among%20these%20notable%20contributions%20was%20food%2C%20namely%2C%20biryani.%20So%20what%20has%20been%20embraced%20today%20as%20Kolkata%20biryani%20in%20fact%20has%20its%20roots%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20the%20city%20of%20%3Cem%3Enawabs%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Manzilat%20Fatima%2C%20the%20great-great-granddaughter%20of%20the%20king%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20the%20characteristic%20of%20Awadh%20biryani%20in%20the%20Kolkata%20one.%20They%20are%20like%20cousins%20of%20one%20family.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-2-1689173481.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manzilat%20Fatima%20is%20the%20great-great-granddaughter%20of%20King%20Wajid%20Ali%20Shah.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-2-1689173481.jpg%