20of%20this%20rather%20unpleasant%20fact%20after%20she%20got%20married.%20Used%20to%20her%20mother%20taking%20impeccable%20care%20of%20her%20clothes%2C%20the%2037-year-old%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20after%20she%20moved%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20got%20married%20in%202015%20and%20used%20to%20wear%20business%20formals%20to%20work.%20My%20mom%20would%20always%20ensure%20that%20my%20clothes%20were%20perfectly%20washed%20and%20ironed.%20When%20we%20had%20to%20set%20up%20a%20house%20after%20marriage%2C%20I%20found%20that%20the%20most%20arduous%20task%20was%20taking%20care%20of%20clothes.%20My%20wardrobe%20was%20a%20mess.%20Many%20of%20my%20clothes%20started%20getting%20ruined%2C%20some%20would%20get%20colour%20on%20them%2C%20and%20some%20would%20shrink.%20I%20was%20very%20frustrated%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gunjan%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20she%20found%20missing%2C%20at%20that%20point%2C%20was%20a%20professional%20laundry%20service.%20Sure%2C%20dry%20cleaners%20existed%2C%20but%20there%20were%20no%20laundromats%2C%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201707px)%20100vw%2C%201707px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDSC07710-min-1688998840-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Laundry%20being%20processed%20at%20a%20Uclean%20Store%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDSC07710-min-1688998840-scaled.jpg%201707w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDSC07710-min-1688998840-200x300.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDSC07710-min-1688998840-500x750.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDSC07710-min-1688998840-768x1152.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDSC07710-min-1688998840-1024x1536.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDSC07710-min-1688998840-1365x2048.jpg%201365w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDSC07710-min-1688998840-150x225.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323275%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20dress%20is%20being%20folded%20at%20a%20UClean%20store.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20her%20husband%20Arunabh%20Sinha%20was%20heading%20the%20North%20India%20business%20of%20a%20budget%20hotel%20chain.%20While%20helping%20them%20expand%20their%20business%20in%20North%20India%2C%20Arunabh%20found%20that%20the%20biggest%20problem%20they%20were%20facing%20across%20the%20country%20was%20laundry%20related.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20get%20complaints%20daily%20regarding%20dirty%20bed%20sheets%2C%20towels%2C%20and%20clothes.%20The%20laundry%20service%20was%20not%20good%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arunabh%2C%20an%20IIT-Bombay%20alumnus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20these%20facts%2C%20the%20couple%20started%20thinking%20of%20launching%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F320745%2Fwoman-scientist-methane-greenhouse-gas-help-farmers-string-bio-startup-ezhil-subbian%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaundry%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20I%20looked%20for%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20laundry%20problem%20in%20the%20hotel%2C%20I%20started%20researching%20the%20market.%20I%20found%20that%20the%20industry%20was%20unorganised%2C%20and%20there%20were%20no%20professional%20players%20other%20than%20our%20neighbourhood%20%3Cem%3Edhobis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20RedSeer%E2%80%99s%20research%20report%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Laundry%20Services%20Market%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20laundry%20market%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20to%20%2415%20billion%20by%202025%E2%80%9D.%20Out%20of%20this%2C%20the%20organised%20sector%20is%20less%20than%20five%20percent%20of%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20take%20up%20the%20opportunity%20to%20organise%20the%20laundry%20industry%20and%20offer%20%E2%80%98quality%20and%20consistent%20services%E2%80%99.%20Arunabh%20quit%20his%20job%20in%20August%202016%2C%20and%20they%20launched%20a%20laundromat%20service%20called%20UClean%20in%20January%202017%20with%20a%20capital%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%2C%20which%20has%20grown%20to%20a%20Rs%20100%20crore%20business%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20microentrepreneurs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-10T195520.867-1688999319.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20uclean%20store%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-10T195520.867-1688999319.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-10T195520.867-1688999319-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-10T195520.867-1688999319-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-10T195520.867-1688999319-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-10T195520.867-1688999319-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323280%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EUClean%20has%20350%2B%20stores%20across%20100%20cities.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20seed%20sown%20in%20their%20minds%20of%20doing%20something%20in%20the%20laundry%20industry%2C%20Faridabad-based%20Gunjan%20and%20Arunabh%20took%20inspiration%20from%20the%20flourishing%20laundromat%20culture%20in%20South%20East%20Asian%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20travelled%20to%20Indonesia%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20Thailand%20and%20Singapore%2C%20and%20found%20the%20laundry%20industry%20thriving.%20Indonesia%20was%20really%20an%20eye-opener.%20In%20India%2C%20most%20give%20their%20clothes%20outside%20for%20ironing.%20So%20we%20wondered%2C%20%E2%80%98Then%20why%20not%20for%20washing%3F%E2%80%99%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20realised%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20more%20of%20a%20supply%20problem%20than%20demand%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Gunjan%2C%20co-founder%20and%20head%20of%20product%20and%20marketing%2C%20UClean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20attempts%20to%20uberise%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321740%2Fmother-daughters-dea-ojasvi-hema-sharma-chilzo-mumbai-global-cuisines-sauces-condiments%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaundry%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20early%202010s%2C%20but%20logistics%20remained%20a%20major%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20these%20laundry%20businesses%20operated%20through%20a%20hub%20and%20spoke%20model.%20They%20had%20their%20factories%20far%20away%20and%20logistics%20ate%20up%20their%20margins.%20Customers%20also%20complained%20about%20delays%20in%20the%20delivery%20of%20laundry.%20There%20was%20also%20an%20issue%20of%20transparency%20and%20trust.%20But%20even%20with%20these%20issues%2C%20people%20were%20giving%20their%20clothes%2C%20which%20showed%20us%20that%20the%20demand%20was%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Gunjan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20they%20decided%20to%20go%20the%20franchise%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20launched%20a%20live%20laundry%20model%20where%20everything%20is%20handled%20hyperlocal.%20Anybody%20can%20visit%20our%20laundromats%20and%20see%20our%20machines%2C%20irons%20and%20detergents%20that%20are%20being%20used.%20You%20can%20see%20how%20your%20clothes%20are%20washed.%20The%20customer%20deserves%20to%20know%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arunabh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20every%20neighbourhood%20is%20different%20in%20India%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20work%20with%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCtrJtxTO8qj%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCtrJtxTO8qj%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCtrJtxTO8qj%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20UClean%20(%40_uclean_)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDynamics%20change%20every%2030%20km.%20We%20would%20have%20to%20customise%20for%20every%20neighbourhood.%20So%20we%20developed%20a%20strategy%20that%20would%20work%20everywhere%20%E2%80%94%20working%20with%20local%20players.%20They%20know%20their%20locale%20well%20and%20what%20people%20want.%20This%20way%2C%20we%20are%20also%20creating%20micro-entrepreneurs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20says%20that%20they%20structured%20an%20existing%20need%20and%20focused%20on%20delivering%20quality.%20They%20knew%20that%20laundry%20is%20an%20essential%20service%20and%20many%20need%20help%20with%20it.%20By%20offering%20a%20simple%2C%20daily%20service%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20earning%20in%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20most%20popular%20service%20is%20%E2%80%98Laundry%20by%20Kg%E2%80%99%20where%20you%20can%20get%20your%20clothes%20%E2%80%98washed%20and%20folded%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98washed%20and%20ironed%E2%80%99.%20They%20also%20offer%20steam%20ironing%2C%20dry%20cleaning%2C%20shoe%2C%20carpet%2C%20sofa%20and%20bag%20cleaning%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20UClean%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F256113%2Fpilot-chef-wat-a-burger-aloo-achari-butter-chicken-desi-flavours-earns-revenue-airline-entrepreneur-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E350%2B%20stores%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20100%20cities%20in%20India.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20they%20became%20the%20fastest%20retail%20chain%20to%20touch%20200%20franchisees%2C%20overtaking%20Subway%2C%20which%20had%20the%20record%2C%20shares%20Gunjan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20always%20found%20dry%20cleaners%20very%20expensive.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20washing%20and%20ironing%20clothes%20took%20the%20majority%20of%20my%20time.%20A%20UClean%20store%20opened%20up%20near%20my%20house%20about%20a%20year%20back%20and%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20regularly%20giving%20my%20clothes%20to%20them.%20It%E2%80%99s%20quick%2C%20clean%2C%20and%20saves%20me%20a%20ton%20of%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Swati%2C%20a%20UClean%20customer%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOvercoming%20social%20stigma%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201168px)%20100vw%2C%201168px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FArunabh-Gunjan-Pic-min-2-1688999531.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221168%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Arunabh%20and%20Gunjan%20started%20Uclean%20in%202017%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FArunabh-Gunjan-Pic-min-2-1688999531.jpeg%201168w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FArunabh-Gunjan-Pic-min-2-1688999531-258x300.jpeg%20258w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FArunabh-Gunjan-Pic-min-2-1688999531-500x581.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FArunabh-Gunjan-Pic-min-2-1688999531-768x893.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FArunabh-Gunjan-Pic-min-2-1688999531-150x174.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323284%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221358%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EArunabh%20and%20Gunjan%20overcame%20several%20challenges%20to%20start%20UClean.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20idea%20was%20great%2C%20the%20couple%20faced%20several%20challenges%2C%20both%20on%20the%20personal%20and%20professional%20front.%20Arunabh%E2%80%99s%20family%20was%20not%20happy%20about%20him%20quitting%20his%20well-paying%20job%20to%20%E2%80%98wash%20people%E2%80%99s%20dirty%20linen%E2%80%99.%20Despite%20having%20run%20a%20successful%20startup%20called%20Franglobal%2C%20he%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20finding%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20at%20a%20very%20well-paying%20job%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20chase%20this%20idea.%20My%20family%20was%20scandalised%20that%20I%20was%20quitting%20my%20job%20to%20%E2%